um%2C%20he%20said%20remote%20workers%20lack%20attachment%2C%20passion%2C%20and%20creativity.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20big%20corporations%20to%20issue%20return%20to%20office%20mandates%20after%20the%202020%20lockdown.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EL'Oreal's%20CEO%20had%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fbusiness%2F2024%2F01%2F17%2Fhome-workers-have-no-creativity-says-loreal-boss%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eharsh%20words%20for%20remote%20workers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%20they%20lack%20attachment%2C%20passion%2C%20or%20creativity%20in%20their%20roles%2C%20during%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20in%20Davos%2C%20Switzerland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20British%20outlet%20the%20Daily%20Telegraph%2C%20Nicolas%20Hieronimus%20%E2%80%94%20a%20French%20businessman%20who%20took%20the%20helm%20of%20the%20cosmetics%20giant%20in%202021%20%E2%80%94%20said%20that%20being%20in%20the%20office%20was%20essential%20for%20the%20company%20and%20its%20employees%20because%20it%20brings%20people%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20so%20many%20employees%20of%20so%20many%20other%20companies%20than%20L'Oreal%20that%20have%20been%20working%20from%20home%20for%20months%2C%20that%20have%20absolutely%20no%20attachment%2C%20no%20passion%2C%20no%20creativity%2C%26quot%3B%20Hieronimus%20said%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20WEF.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20reasons%20that%20we%20hit%20the%20ground%20running%20after%20COVID%20is%20that%20we%20did%20not%20do%20like%20many%20tech%20companies%20and%20say%20everybody%20works%20from%20home%20all%20the%20time%2C%20and%20now%20they%20say%3A%20'Oh%20my%20God%2C%20that%20was%20a%20mistake%2C%20please%20come%20back.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EL'Oreal%20requires%20employees%20to%20be%20in%20the%20office%20at%20least%20three%20days%20a%20week%20currently%20and%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20companies%20to%20issue%20return-to-office%20mandates%20after%20the%20lockdown%20in%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floreal-us-ceo-reveals-why-company-forcing-workers-back-office-2020-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EL'Oreal%20USA's%20former%20CEO%20Stephane%20Rinderknech%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20the%20company's%2011%2C000%20employees%20back%20to%20the%20office%20in%20a%20staggered%20process%20in%20July%202020.%20He%20said%20in%20a%20memo%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20life%20of%20this%20company%20is%20based%20on%20the%20sensorial%20enrichment%20of%20experiencing%20beauty%20in%20person.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20world%20of%20beauty%20is%20not%20a%20remote%20or%20virtual%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20faced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsome-loreal-workers-say-gaslighting-office-photos-belie-reality-2020-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebacklash%20from%20employees%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20mandate%20with%20one%20worker%20in%20California%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BThey%20keep%20repeating%20how%20positive%20people%20are%20reacting%20and%20it's%20bullshit%20because%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20go%20back%E2%80%A6It's%20pure%20gaslighting.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Hieronimus%20said%20at%20the%20WEF%20that%20it's%20%26quot%3Bvital%20to%20be%20in%20the%20office%26quot%3B%20for%20serendipity%20and%20having%20the%20chance%20to%20meet%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20it's%20also%20more%20fair%20to%20workers%20because%20we%20have%20lots%20of%20young%20people%20who%20have%20small%20houses%20or%20have%20young%20kids%20and%20working%20from%20home%20is%20actually%20very%20bad%20for%20their%20mental%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20vital%20for%20the%20company%2C%20and%20it's%20vital%20for%20the%20employees.%20It's%20also%20fair%20to%20the%20blue%20collar%20workers%20that%20work%20every%20day%20in%20the%20factory.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-work-rto-billionaire-ceo-threaten-fire-workers-wfh-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECEOs%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20changed%20their%20tune%20on%20remote%20work%20since%20the%20pandemic%20saying%20that%20employees%20are%20more%20productive%20and%20efficient%20in%20the%20office.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENumerous%20firms%20including%20Google%2C%20Meta%2C%20Starbucks%2C%20and%20JPMorgan%20have%20walked%20back%20their%20remote%20working%20policies%20as%20a%20result%2C%20and%20are%20requiring%20workers%20to%20come%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-making-workers-employees-return-to-office-rto-wfh-hybrid-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eback%20to%20the%20office%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20research%20to%20back%20up%20some%20of%20the%20claims%20made%20by%20CEOs.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femployees-back-to-the-office-what-the-data-really-says-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EOne%202023%20study%20of%20200%20data%20entry%20workers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Chennai%2C%20India%20by%20the%20National%20Bureau%20of%20Economic%20Research%20found%20that%20the%20productivity%20of%20workers%20randomly%20assigned%20to%20work%20from%20home%20was%2018%25%20lower%20than%20their%20in-office%20counterparts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-workers-lack-passion-and-creativity-loreal-ceo-says-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705921858000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ae3826dcdb354a9859821f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-workers-lack-passion-and-creativity-loreal-ceo-says-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%