with%20gunshots.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20curfew.%20Now%20there%20will%20be%20Deepotsav%20and%20Ramotsav%20here.%20Shri%20Ram's%20name%20'Sankirtan'%20will%20echo%20in%20the%20streets%20because%20the%20establishment%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20here%20is%20the%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FKigqt3UVVm%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FKigqt3UVVm%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1749351073729679550%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2022%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNobody%20will%20become%20a%20hurdle%20in%20Ayodhya's%20parikrama%20any%20more.%20Ayodhya's%20alleys%20will%20not%20echo%20with%20the%20sound%20of%20bullets%20any%20more.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20curfew.%20Now%2C%20Deepotsav%20and%20Ramotsav%20will%20be%20held.%20Ram%20kirtans%20will%20echo%20in%20the%20alleys%20because%20the%20establishment%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20here%20today%20also%20marks%20the%20announcement%20of%20Ram%20Rajya%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adityanath%20said%20while%20addressing%20the%20gathering%20after%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20was%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20Mr%20Adityanath%20is%20the%20only%20BJP%20Chief%20Minister%20to%20attend%20the%20grand%20event%20and%20was%20also%20present%20inside%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20of%20the%20temple%20during%20the%20rituals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20reference%20to%20the%201990%20incidents%20was%20a%20veiled%20attack%20on%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20the%20main%20opposition%20in%20the%20state%20now%20led%20by%20Mr%20Yadav's%20son%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Akhilesh%20Singh%20Yadav.%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20who%20was%20invited%20for%20the%20ceremony%20today%2C%20has%20said%20he%20would%20visit%20the%20temple%20later.%20Mr%20Adityanath's%20remarks%20also%20come%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20Opposition%20leaders%2C%20including%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20staying%20away%20from%20today's%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Happened%20In%201990%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%20had%20gained%20steam%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Rath%20Yatra%20led%20by%20BJP%20veteran%20Lal%20Krishna%20Advani.%20At%20Ayodhya%2C%20the%20situation%20was%20heating%20up.%20As%20leaders%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20Sangh%20Parivar%20started%20mobilising%20people%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20had%20deployed%20force%20in%20large%20numbers.%20%26quot%3BNo%20bird%20would%20be%20able%20to%20fly%20into%20Ayodhya%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20famously%20said%20then.%20On%20October%2030%2C%20large%20numbers%20of%20devotees%20walked%20to%20Ayodhya%20after%20state%20police%20blocked%20bus%20and%20train%20services.%20The%20protesters%20clashed%20with%20cops%20on%20the%20road%20leading%20to%20the%20now-demolished%20Babri%20Masjid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20a%20sadhu%20took%20control%20of%20a%20security%20bus%20and%20drove%20through%20the%20barricades.%20The%20cops%20responded%20by%20chasing%20down%20the%20protesters%20and%20cracking%20down%20forcefully.%20Similar%20clashes%20took%20place%20on%20November%201%20and%20a%20total%20of%20at%20least%2017%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20police%20firing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Aftermath%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20government%20came%20under%20criticism%20for%20the%20police%20firing.%20In%20response%2C%20he%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bpainful%2C%20yet%20necessary%26quot%3B%20decision%20and%20referred%20to%20the%20high%20court%20ruling%20to%20maintain%20peace%20at%20the%20disputed%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20year%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20lost%20the%20Assembly%20election%20and%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power.%20Kalyan%20Singh%20was%20named%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20it%20was%20under%20his%20tenure%20that%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20was%20demolished%20on%20December%206%2C%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22