eskov%20condemned%20the%20%26quot%3Bbestial%20face%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Kyiv%20regime%2C%20alleging%20attacks%20on%20civil%20infrastructure%20and%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-blames-kyiv-for-attack-on-baltic-gas-terminal%2Farticleshow%2F107052518.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-blames-kyiv-for-attack-on-baltic-gas-terminal%2Famp_articleshow%2F107052518.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-blames-kyiv-for-attack-on-baltic-gas-terminal%2Famp_articleshow%2F107052518.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Not%20Slaves%2C%20But%20Coolies'%3A%20Must%20Confront%20Questions%20'Government-Sponsored'%20Labour%20Export%20Raises%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F21173418%2FEffect-40.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Do%20you%20mean%20slaves%2C%20sir%3F%E2%80%99%20Mr.%20Burnham%20winced.%20%E2%80%98Why%20no%2C%20Reid.%20Not%20slaves%20%E2%80%93%20coolies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHave%20you%20not%20heard%20it%20said%20that%20when%20God%20closes%20one%20door%20he%20opens%20another%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThose%20lines%20from%20Amitav%20Ghosh%E2%80%99s%20poignant%20work%20of%20fiction%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESea%20of%20Poppies%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20told%20the%20story%20of%20Indian%20indentured%20labour%20shipped%20out%20of%20their%20poverty%20in%20British%20India%20and%20sent%20into%20slavery%20on%20sugar%20plantations%20in%20the%20Mauritius.%20Slavery%20had%20been%20officially%20abolished%20by%20the%20imperial%20government%20but%20it%20actively%20supported%20and%20made%20legal%20the%20export%20of%20contractual%20labour%2C%20coolies%20who%20ended%20up%20living%20the%20life%20of%20slaves.%20Many%20works%20of%20fiction%20and%20non-fiction%20have%20been%20inspired%20by%20the%20tragic%20story%20of%20indentured%20labour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20one%20must%20rightly%20condemn%20these%20inhuman%20excesses%20of%20colonialism%20and%20racism%2C%20it%20is%20useful%20to%20remember%20that%20Indian%20%E2%80%98coolies%E2%80%99%20continue%20to%20be%20exported%20to%20the%20global%20market%20for%20wage%20labour.%20The%20Indian%20working%20class%20in%20free%20India%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20resist%20the%20temptation%20of%20overseas%20employment%20given%20the%20shortage%20of%20employment%20at%20home%20and%20inadequate%20remuneration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20issue%20of%20%E2%80%98government-sponsored%E2%80%99%20labour%20export%20has%20once%20again%20made%20news%20with%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20reportedly%20negotiating%20agreements%20with%20the%20governments%20of%20Israel%20and%20Taiwan%20to%20export%20unemployed%20semi-skilled%20and%20skilled%20Indian%20workers%20to%20these%20labour-seeking%20economies.%20As%20many%20as%20ten%20trades%20union%20have%20opposed%20this%20planned%20export%20to%20Israel%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20worker%20safety%20since%20they%20would%20be%20heading%20into%20a%20conflict%20zone.%20Such%20concern%20and%20opposition%20has%20not%20stayed%20the%20hand%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20in%20Haryana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20desperation%20of%20the%20working%20class%20was%20echoed%20recently%20in%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20Rohtak%2C%20echoing%20the%20agonies%20of%20erstwhile%20indentured%20labour%2C%20where%20many%20had%20lined%20up%20to%20register%20for%20jobs%20in%20Israel%2C%20willing%20to%20even%20work%20in%20bombed%20out%20Gaza%20risking%20their%20life%20for%20a%20few%20Dollars%20more.%20A%20Reuters%20report%20quoted%20a%20worker%20who%20had%20lined%20up%20for%20a%20job%20in%20Israel%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20it%E2%80%99s%20in%20our%20destiny%20to%20die%2C%20then%20we%20can%20die%20either%20here%20or%20there.%20My%20hope%20is%20that%20we%20will%20go%20and%20do%20good%20work%20and%20spend%20some%20time%20and%20come%20back.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVivek%20Sharma%2C%20the%2028-year-old%20mason%20quoted%20by%20Reuters%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20I%20am%20aware%20of%20the%20conflict%2C%20but%20I%20can%20earn%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20in%20a%20short%20time.%E2%80%9D%20Sharma%20hoped%20to%20earn%20in%20a%20year%20%2412%2C000%20and%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20could%20take%20me%20at%20least%20five%20years%20to%20earn%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20money%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%20Wage%20differentials%20have%20been%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20Indian%20labour%20export%20for%20several%20decades%20now.%20Israel%20is%20seeking%20masons%2C%20painters%2C%20electricians%2C%20plumbers%20and%20farmer%20labour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnehru-patel-treated-china-as-equal-modi-has-conceded-a-power-differential%5C%22%3ENehru-Patel%20Treated%20China%20as%20Equal%2C%20Modi%20Has%20Conceded%20a%20Power%20Differential%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEuropean%20colonialism%20has%20ended%20but%20the%20global%20demand%20for%20desperate%20Indian%20labour%20has%20not.%20The%20export%20of%20labour%20has%20been%20a%20key%20element%20of%20Indian%20trade%20policy%20since%20the%201970s%20when%20it%20was%20realised%20that%20homeward%20Dollar%20remittances%20from%20overseas%20workers%20were%20contributing%20to%20balance%20of%20payments%20management%20while%20easing%20pressures%20in%20the%20domestic%20labour%20market.%20Kerala%20was%20the%20first%20state%20to%20benefit%20from%20this%20external%20demand%20for%20wage%20labour.%20Its%20unemployed%20workers%20were%20readily%20absorbed%20into%20the%20Gulf%20labour%20market.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGulf%20remittances%20have%20not%20only%20helped%20the%20economy%20of%20industrially%20backward%20Kerala%20but%20have%20become%20an%20important%20source%20of%20foreign%20exchange%20for%20the%20economy%20as%20a%20whole.%20Last%20year%20total%20inward%20remittances%20amounted%20to%20US%24125%20billion%2C%20a%20fifth%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20exchange%20reserves.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESoon%20after%20Israel%20indicated%20an%20interest%20in%20importing%20Indian%20labour%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Ftaiwan-set-to-hire-1-lakh-indian-workers-india-taiwan-pact-india-china-relations%2Farticleshow%2F105118104.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3ETaiwan%20too%20began%20negotiating%20with%20Indian%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20representatives%2C%20willing%20to%20provide%20employment%20for%20a%20100%2C000%20Indians%20at%20wage%20rates%20comparable%20to%20what%20local%20workers%20are%20paid.%20Taiwan%E2%80%99s%20minimum%20wage%20is%20reportedly%20%24820%20per%20month.%20This%20compares%20very%20well%20with%20whatever%20even%20a%20skilled%20labourer%20can%20make%20in%20India.%20Taiwan%E2%80%99s%20Premier%20Chen%20Chien-jen%20and%20India%20Taipei%20Association%E2%80%99s%20director%20general%20Manharsinh%20Laxmanbhai%20Yadav%20have%20signed%20a%20memorandum%20of%20understanding%20to%20facilitate%20labour%20mobility.%20Now%20that%20the%20ruling%20party%20is%20back%20in%20power%20one%20must%20expect%20this%20MoU%20to%20go%20forward.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETaiwan%20is%20reportedly%20looking%20to%20hire%20imported%20workers%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20sector%20as%20well%20as%20on%20construction%20projects%2C%20agricultural%20and%20fish%20farms%20and%20as%20household%20workers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Israel%20and%20Taiwan%20have%20been%20in%20the%20news%2C%20Indian%20labour%20has%20headed%20wherever%20it%20could%20secure%20employment%2C%20including%20South-east%20Asia%2C%20given%20that%20overseas%20wages%20in%20most%20labour-deficient%20economies%20would%20be%20higher%20than%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20labour-surplus%20markets.%20While%20Indians%20complain%20about%20illegal%20immigration%20of%20Bangladeshis%20and%20Rohingyas%2C%20many%20around%20the%20world%20are%20complaining%20about%20such%20illegal%20migration%20of%20Indians.%20According%20to%20United%20States%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%20data%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2F5x-hike-in-illegal-indian-immigrants-to-the-us-nearly-97000-caught-over-past-year-us-data%5C%22%3E96%2C917%20Indians%20were%20apprehended%20seeking%20to%20illegally%20enter%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20search%20of%20livelihood%20between%20October%202022%20and%20September%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fhow-india-made-virtue-out-of-necessity-by-exporting-labour%5C%22%3EHow%20India%20Made%20Virtue%20Out%20of%20Necessity%20by%20Exporting%20Labour%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETill%20recently%20Indian%20workers%20in%20many%20Gulf%20kingdoms%20were%20treated%20no%20better%20than%20the%20indentured%20labourers%20of%20the%20colonial%20era.%20They%20were%20not%20only%20cheated%20by%20touts%20at%20home%2C%20as%20in%20the%20case%20of%20indentured%20labour%2C%20but%20made%20to%20live%20in%20inhuman%20conditions%20in%20host%20countries%2C%20with%20no%20rights%20and%20no%20voice.%20To%20be%20fair%2C%20one%20cannot%20equate%20the%20conditions%20of%20the%2021st%20Century%20contractual%20labour%20migrant%20to%20the%20desperate%20condition%20of%20the%2019th%20and%20early%2020th%20Century%20indentured%20labourer.%20The%20interests%20of%20the%20former%20are%20protected%20by%20international%20law%20and%20bilateral%20treaties%2C%20but%20this%20was%20not%20always%20so.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20while%20Indian%20politicians%2C%20diplomats%20and%20officials%20can%20wax%20eloquent%20today%20about%20the%20inhumanity%20of%20the%20colonial%20system%2C%20they%20are%20all%20too%20aware%20of%20the%20inhumanity%20of%20working%20conditions%20till%20recently%20in%20many%20countries%20where%20Indian%20diplomats%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20function%20as%20labour%20representatives%2C%20seeking%20better%20working%20conditions%20for%20Indian%20citizens.%20One%20former%20Indian%20ambassador%20posted%20in%20a%20Gulf%20kingdom%20told%20me%20that%20his%20was%20not%20a%20%E2%80%98diplomatic%20assignment%E2%80%99%2C%20he%20was%20functioning%20as%20a%20labour%20relations%20officer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20state%20governments%20may%20encourage%20their%20unemployed%20workers%20to%20go%20overseas%2C%20it%20is%20incumbent%20on%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20protect%20the%20economic%20and%20social%20interests%20of%20Indian%20workers%20overseas%2C%20especially%20if%20such%20workers%20are%20being%20exported%20as%20a%20result%20of%20bilateral%20agreements%20between%20governments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20interesting%20to%20note%20that%20even%20within%20the%20British%20empire%20officials%20in%20the%20colonies%20dealing%20with%20requisitioning%20and%20supply%20of%20migrant%20labour%20differed%20with%20those%20viewing%20the%20matter%20from%20afar%20in%20London.%20It%20was%20the%20influence%20of%20plantation%20interests%20that%20swayed%20policy%20from%20time%20to%20time%20till%20finally%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E1910%20the%20Secretary%20of%20State%20for%20the%20Colonies%20in%20London%20directed%20that%20emigration%20of%20indentured%20labour%20be%20discontinued%2C%20or%20that%20at%20least%20the%20government%20ought%20not%20to%20be%20party%20to%20it%2C%20and%20that%20planters%20be%20allowed%20to%20obtain%20free%20labour%20from%20India%20without%20any%20government%20assistance%20or%20interference.%20This%20suggestion%20was%20rejected%20by%20the%20government%20of%20India%20in%20Calcutta.%20It%20was%20only%20in%201915%20that%20the%20imperial%20government%20finally%20managed%20to%20abolish%20the%20system%20of%20indentured%20labour.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Israel-Taiwan%20demand%20for%20Indian%20labour%20helps%20to%20highlight%20an%20issue%20that%20will%20not%20go%20away%20any%20time%20soon.%20This%20is%20the%20global%20shortage%20of%20semi-skilled%20and%20skilled%20labour%20in%20many%20countries%20and%20the%20desperate%20desire%20of%20many%20Indians%20to%20migrate%20in%20search%20of%20better%20income.%20If%20this%20is%20not%20legally%20permitted%2C%20the%20migration%20will%20go%20underground%2C%20as%20it%20has%20already%20done.%20Illegal%20migration%20out%20of%20India%20and%20into%20developed%20economies%20has%20risen%20and%20was%20recently%20highlighted%20by%20the%20French%20stopping%20a%20plane%20enroute%20to%20Nicaragua%20full%20of%20Indians%20hoping%20to%20end%20up%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20can%20celebrate%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Indian%20diaspora%2C%20the%20community%20of%20overseas%20Indians%2C%20is%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20biggest%2C%20having%20recently%20out-numbered%20the%20Chinese%20diaspora.%20However%2C%20one%20must%20differentiate%20between%20those%20Indians%20who%20may%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20migrate%20decades%20ago%20as%20indentured%20labour%20but%20are%20now%20happily%20settled%20in%20their%20host%20countries%2C%20middle%20class%20migrants%20who%20are%20living%20comfortable%20lives%20overseas%2C%20and%20a%20working%20class%20migrating%20in%20desperation%2C%20for%20a%20few%20Dollars%20more.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESanjaya%20Baru%20is%20an%20economist%2C%20a%20former%20newspaper%20editor%2C%20a%20best-selling%20author%2C%20and%20former%20adviser%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Manmohan%20Singh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705918535000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fw