tyle-creep-income-increase-raise-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Article%20355%2C%20A%20Step%20Away%20From%20President's%20Rule%2C%20In%20Manipur%20Now%3A%20Opposition%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20all-party%20meeting%20in%20crisis-hit%20Manipur%20has%20asked%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20state%20government%20to%20scrap%20the%20tripartite%20suspension%20of%20operations%20(SoO)%20signed%20with%2025%20Kuki%20insurgent%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20security%20forces%20will%20be%20able%20to%20launch%20a%20full-scale%20operation%20against%20the%20Kuki%20insurgents%20once%20the%20SoO%20is%20removed%2C%20the%20parties%20said%20in%20the%20meeting%20chaired%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20who%20belongs%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20all-party%20meeting%20including%20the%20Opposition%20criticised%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20state%20government%20for%20not%20telling%20the%20public%20that%20Article%20355%20of%20the%20Constitution%20has%20been%20applied%20in%20Manipur%20since%20ethnic%20clashes%20broke%20out%20in%20May%202023%20between%20the%20hill-majority%20Kuki%20tribes%20and%20the%20valley-majority%20Meiteis%20over%20disagreements%20on%20land%2C%20resources%2C%20political%20representation%2C%20and%20affirmative%20action%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20Congress%20chief%20K%20Meghachandra%20Singh%20said%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20told%20all%20the%20parties%20in%20the%20meeting%20about%20the%20Article%20355%20matter.%20The%20Congress%20leader%20expressed%20concern%20over%20why%20the%20state%20and%20the%20Centre%20never%20revealed%20this%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20reflects%20the%20insincerity%20of%20both%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20state%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20Meghachandra%20Singh%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Chief%20Minister%20told%20us%20Article%20355%20has%20been%20enforced%20in%20Manipur.%20There%20was%20no%20clarity%20on%20this%20before.%20It%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20took%20so%20long%20to%20tell%20us%20this.%20Both%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20state%20government%20are%20not%20sincere%2C%20we%20know%20now%2C%20it%20is%20confirmed.%20Both%20external%20aggression%20and%20internal%20disturbance%20are%20covered%20under%20Article%20355%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters%20in%20Imphal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%20355%20of%20the%20Constitution%20says%20the%20Centre%20must%20protect%20states%20against%20external%20aggression%20and%20internal%20disturbance%20to%20ensure%20government%20stability.%20It%20allows%20the%20Centre%20to%20take%20charge%20of%20a%20state's%20law%20and%20order%20enforcement%20without%20dismissing%20the%20government%2C%20and%20is%20considered%20a%20step%20below%20the%20President's%20rule%2C%20which%20give%20full%20control%20to%20the%20President.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F13k1v6cg_moreh_625x300_20_January_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Manipur%20Security%20Adviser%20Kuldiep%20Singh%20told%20reporters%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20can%20call%20a%20meeting%20anytime%20of%20the%20unified%20command%20that's%20looking%20after%20law%20and%20order%20in%20the%20state.%20However%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20name%20was%20missing%20from%20the%20list%20of%20names%20who%20are%20part%20of%20the%20unified%20command.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20led%20to%20speculation%20that%20Article%20355%20was%20in%20effect%2C%20and%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20laid%20the%20matter%20to%20rest%20by%20confirming%20it%20in%20the%20all-party%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuki-Zo%20tribes%20have%20been%20demanding%20President's%20rule%20in%20Manipur.%20They%20say%20Pr