mer%20offshore%20oil%20and%20gas%20consultant%20from%20Watford%2C%20United%20Kingdom.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20traveled%20and%20been%20around%20people%20from%20other%20nations%20%E2%80%94%20American%2C%20German%2C%20Swiss%2C%20French%2C%20and%20many%20UK%20people.%20Two%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20I%20was%2073%20and%20living%20in%20Spain%2C%20I%20started%20exploring%20my%20long-term%20retirement%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20a%20place%20in%20Spain%20for%20nearly%2040%20years.%20My%20father%20was%20in%20a%20care%20home%20there.%20It%20had%20all%20the%20amenities%20and%20the%20support%2C%20but%20I'd%20never%20been%20able%20to%20make%20Spanish%20friends.%20That%2C%20and%20the%20cost%2C%20made%20me%20decide%20not%20to%20retire%20to%20Spain%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EChoosing%20where%20I%20wanted%20to%20retire%20abroad%20was%20difficult%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20against%20a%20care%20home%20in%20the%20UK%20for%20myself.%20Some%20can%20be%20very%20good%3B%20some%20can%20be%20very%20bad.%20I%20also%20found%20it%20too%20expensive.%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3EWhen%20I%20was%20growing%20up%20in%20the%201960s%20and%201970s%2C%20folks%20had%20respect%20for%20their%20elders.%20That%20has%20changed%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20could%20impact%20the%20care%20you'd%20receive%20in%20a%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20then%20spent%20six%20months%20in%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20but%20I%20found%20that%20to%20be%20very%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmerica%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20New%20Zealand%20were%20very%20nice%20but%20expensive.%20If%20I%20wanted%20to%20retire%20somewhere%20I%20could%20save%20my%20pennies%2C%20Thailand%20came%20out%20on%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20decided%20on%20Thailand%2C%20I%20did%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20tour%20of%20other%20Asian%20countries.%20I%20traveled%20to%20Vietnam%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20and%20Malaysia.%20I'd%20also%20worked%20all%20over%20Asia%20from%20around%201975%20for%2020%20years%20as%20part%20of%20my%20job%20in%20oil%20and%20gas%20and%20building%20hotels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI'll%20see%20my%20family%20less%2C%20but%20it%20hasn't%20influenced%20my%20decision%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20three%20grandchildren%3A%20two%2019-year-old%20boys%20and%20a%2015-year-old%20girl.%20But%20they%20want%20to%20do%20their%20own%20thing%2C%20even%20when%20you%20visit.%20I%20only%20saw%20them%20once%20a%20week%20when%20I%20lived%20in%20the%20UK.%20My%20family's%20reaction%20when%20I%20said%20I%20would%20retire%20in%20Thailand%20was%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20come%20to%20see%20you.%20It's%20far%20too%20far%20away.%26quot%3B%20You%20can't%20say%20anything%20to%20that%3B%20they're%20quite%20correct.%20But%20I%20will%20visit%20back%20home%20once%20or%20twice%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20here%20are%20very%20respectful.%20They%20respect%20their%20elders%2C%20whereas%20you%20don't%20get%20that%20in%20other%20European%20countries.%20In%20Thailand%2C%20when%20I'm%20just%20getting%20on%20and%20off%20the%20bus%2C%20younger%20people%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20sit%20here%2C%20and%20I'll%20stand.%26quot%3B%20It%20can%20happen%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20but%20people%20generally%20will%20not%20move.%20Plus%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20food%20in%20Thailand%2C%20you%20have%20a%20great%20selection%20%E2%80%94%20with%20Thai%20food%2C%20the%20world%20is%20your%20lobster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20different%20visas%20for%20people%20wanting%20to%20move%20to%20Thailand.%20I%20have%20a%20retirement%20visa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20had%20to%20consider%20medical%20facilities%20in%20Thailand%20when%20finding%20a%20home%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20town's%20population%20should%20be%20considered%20when%20making%20a%20choice.%20The%20main%20areas%20expats%20live%20in%20are%20Bangkok%2C%20Chiang%20Mai%2C%20Hua%20Hin%2C%20and%20Pattaya.%20In%20the%20main%20towns%2C%20lots%20of%20people%20understand%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20have%20to%20consider%20the%20hospitals%20in%20these%20areas%20because%20we're%20a%20bit%20older.%20Private%20medical%20insurance%20is%20very%20easy%20to%20sort.%20In%20the%20UK's%20smaller%20towns%2C%20you%20always%20have%20to%20queue.%20In%20Thailand%2C%20you%20walk%20straight%20in%20and%20straight%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20retirement%20and%20care%20facility%2C%20they%20also%20help%20you%20get%20set%20up%20with%20medical%20insurance.%20I've%20had%20a%20couple%20of%20accidents%2C%20and%20within%20minutes%2C%20the%20on-site%20staff%20are%20with%20you%2C%20looking%20after%20you%2C%20taking%20you%20to%20a%20hospital%20if%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20chose%20the%20city%20of%20Hua%20Hin%20because%20it%20has%20many%20weekend%20visitors%20from%20Bangkok%20and%20other%20folk%20so%20there%20are%20more%20services%20and%20amenities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20moved%20into%20the%20Sunshine%20International%20Retiree%20Resort%20in%20September%20last%20year.%20The%20resort%20offers%20private%20rooms%20with%20medical%20care%20packages%20should%20you%20need%20them.%20Then%20there's%20a%20free%20shuttle%20into%20the%20town%2C%20a%20pool%20and%20restaurant%2C%20room%20service%20if%20you%20want%2C%20and%20different%20activities%20each%20evening%20like%20barbecues%20and%20cocktail%20nights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20friends%20out%20here%20are%20mainly%20British%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20made%20a%20few%20Thai%20friends%2C%20but%20generally%20speaking%2C%20in%20the%20resort%2C%20folk%20keep%20to%20themselves%2C%20which%20goes%20around%20the%20world.%20You%20have%20a%20German%20group%2C%20a%20French%20group%2C%20and%20a%20UK%20group%20%E2%80%94%20my%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20an%20average%20day%2C%20I%20generally%20make%20my%20own%20breakfast%20and%20swim%20and%20sunbathe%20because%20the%20temperature%20is%2027%C2%B0C%20to%2030%C2%B0C%20every%20day.%20You%20certainly%20don't%20get%20that%20in%20the%20UK.%20Even%20in%20Spain%2C%20it's%20quite%20chilly%20in%20January.%20But%20as%20a%20retiree%2C%20your%20daily%20life%20is%20generally%20the%20same%20wherever%20you%20are%20in%20the%20world.%20I%20don't%20do%20much%20else%20other%20than%20swim%2C%20sunbathe%2C%20and%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20thing%20I%20miss%20from%20the%20UK%20are%20historic%20British%20buildings.%20There%20are%20temples%2C%20but%20you%20can't%20find%20medieval%20architecture%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20my%20friends%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20most%20of%20them%20aren't%20with%20us%20any%20longer.%20Even%20when%20I%20was%20back%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20I%20didn't%20get%20invited%20to%20things%20as%20a%20single%20person.%20At%20the%20resort%2C%20you%20can%20meet%20people%20and%20share%20a%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-abroad-thailand-cheaper-respectful-retiree-resort-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705917967000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a943606979d737182447e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-abroad-thailand-cheaper-respectful-retiree-resort-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2075-year-old%20British%20retiree%20shares%20why%20he%20moved%20into%20a%20retirement%20resort%20in%20Thailand.%20He%20said%20affordability%20and%20medical%20care%20were%20driving%20factors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Root)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A37%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-abroad-thailand-cheaper-respectful-retiree-resort-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20is%20your%20grocery%20delivery%20taking%20so%20long%3F%20Your%20driver%20has%202%20other%20deliveries.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20shopper%20wearing%20a%20baseball%20cap%20loads%20several%20cases%20of%20bottled%20water%20onto%20an%20orange%20flat-bed%20cart%20at%20a%20Costco%20store.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6516fd34f5d0bb0019e5b9cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222688%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShoppers%20for%20Instacart%2C%20Walmart%20Spark%2C%20and%20other%20gig%20delivery%20services%20say%20batching%20orders%20weighs%20down%20their%20earnings.%3Cp%3EPATRICK%20T.%20FALLON%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDelivery%20apps%20like%20Instacart%20and%20Walmart%20Spark%20often%C2%A0'batch'%20orders%20together.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20gig%20workers%20say%20it%20cuts%20into%20their%20income%20since%20they%20get%20paid%20less%20for%20each%20order%20delivered.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECustomers%20can%20also%20get%20frustrated%20waiting%20for%20an%20order%20to%20show%20up.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20summer%2C%20some%20gig%20workers%20who%20delivered%20grocery%20orders%20for%20Walmart%20noticed%20a%20change%3A%20Instead%20of%20just%20delivering%20one%20order%2C%20they%20had%20to%20deliver%20two%20or%20three%20at%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThree%20grocery%20orders%20can%20also%20be%20delivered%20during%20each%20trip%20by%20using%20your%20front%20seat%2C%20back%20seat%2C%20and%20trunk%20space%20to%20keep%20these%20orders%20separate%2C%26quot%3B%20Walmart%20told%20workers%20for%20its%20Spark%20service%20at%20the%20time%20in%20an%20email.%20The%20advice%20is%20now%20on%20the%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrive4spark-walmart.helpdocs.io%2Fl%2Fen%2Farticle%2Fpmpzf3r7s7-understanding-offer-types%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewebsite%20for%20Spark%20drivers.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20practice%20of%20bundling%20orders%20isn't%20new.%20Other%20apps%2C%20including%20Instacart%20and%20DoorDash%2C%20have%20been%20doing%20it%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20four%20independent%20contractors%20who%20make%20the%20deliveries%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20practice%20usually%20leaves%20them%20doing%20more%20work%20for%20less%20money%2C%20further%20eroding%20their%20earning%20potential%20on%20gig-work%20apps.%20The%20workers%20declined%20to%20have%20their%20names%20used%2C%20but%20BI%20verified%20their%20identities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgolden-age-gig-work-instacart-doordash-delivery-jobs-over-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Egig%20workers%20say%20that%20their%20earnings%20have%20fallen%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20past%20year%20because%20of%20lower%20pay%20and%20greater%20competition%20among%20drivers%20for%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDrivers%20have%20a%20choice%2C%20companies%20say%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBatches%20have%20been%20part%20of%20Instacart's%20strategy%20for%20%26quot%3Bseveral%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20company%20spokesperson%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBatches%20that%20include%20orders%20from%20multiple%20stores%20make%20up%20a%20very%20low%20percentage%20of%20batches%20on%20our%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Instacart%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20with%20any%20batch%2C%20shoppers%20are%20never%20required%20to%20select%20multi-order%20or%20multi-store%20batches.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBatches%20with%20multiple%20orders%20are%20%26quot%3Bcompensated%20accordingly%20and%20reflect%20the%20effort%20it%20will%20take%20to%20fulfill%20those%20batches%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBatching%20is%20a%20win%20for%20drivers%20and%20our%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Walmart%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BDrivers%20often%20prefer%20offers%20for%20batched%20deliveries%20and%20receive%20higher%20average%20earnings%20per%20trip%20while%20spending%20less%20time%20per%20delivery.%20Batching%20is%20also%20a%20way%20to%20serve%20more%20customers%20more%20efficiently%20and%20accurately.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20proud%20to%20offer%20multiple%20types%20of%20deliveries%2C%20and%20drivers%20can%20choose%20which%20offers%20to%20accept%20based%20on%20their%20preferences%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20DoorDash%20spokesperson%20did%20not%20provide%20comment%20for%20this%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDrivers%20find%20angry%20customers%2C%20lower%20ratings%2C%20lost%20tips%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experience%20can%20be%20frustrating%20for%20customers.%20Customers%20can%20track%20where%20their%20driver%20is%20using%20the%20Walmart%20app%2C%20but%20they%20have%20no%20clue%20when%20their%20driver%20has%20more%20than%20one%20order%20to%20deliver%2C%20one%20Spark%20driver%20in%20Alabama%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20customers%20get%20angry%20wondering%20why%20it's%20taking%20so%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Alabama%20driver%20said.%20%26quot%3BOn%20their%20end%2C%20they%20just%20see%20a%20vehicle%20driving%20all%20over%20the%20city%20with%20their%20groceries%20in%20it.%26quot%3B%20In%20reality%2C%20the%20driver%20is%20following%20a%20route%20created%20by%20Walmart%20to%20deliver%20the%20orders%2C%20and%20someone's%20order%20has%20to%20be%20delivered%20last.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20give%20drivers%20low%20ratings%20and%20pull%20away%20tips%20as%20a%20result%2C%20the%20driver%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalmart%20also%20batches%20together%20orders%20of%20non-perishable%20goods%2C%20such%20as%20shampoo%20and%20electronics%2C%20often%20combining%20a%20dozen%20or%20more%20orders%20together%20for%20one%20driver%20to%20deliver.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20trying%20to%20be%20like%20FedEx%20and%20UPS%2C%20but%20they'll%20put%2010%20orders%20in%20one%20whole%20trip%2C%20and%20you%20might%20get%20%2424%20to%20%2430%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20Spark%20driver%20in%20North%20Carolina%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pay%20can%20be%20reasonable%20if%20the%20delivery%20addresses%20are%20close%20together%2C%20the%20driver%20said.%20But%20if%20they're%20more%20spread%20out%2C%20the%20deliveries%20take%20more%20time%2C%20making%20it%20less%20profitable%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Instacart%2C%20shoppers%20used%20to%20shop%20and%20deliver%20one%20order%20at%20a%20time.%20But%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstacarts-profitability-relies-on-batching-orders-its-shoppers-hate-it-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EInstacart%20has%20bundled%20two%20or%20three%20deliveries%20together%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20bundling%2C%20known%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbatch%26quot%3B%20in%20Instacart%20lingo%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20ways%20it%20improved%20its%20profitability%20ahead%20of%20its%20IPO%20last%20September%2C%20it%20said%20in%20filings%20with%20the%20SEC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20Instacart%20shopper%20in%20New%20York%20City%20said%20that%20they%20make%20less%20per%20order%20when%20they%20deliver%20a%20batch%20of%20two%20or%20three%20at%20once%20instead%20of%20a%20single%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20complicated%20%E2%80%93%20and%20generally%20less%20profitable%20%E2%80%93%20are%20batches%20that%20involve%20shopping%20multiple%20orders%20at%20different%20stores%2C%20then%20delivering%20them%20to%20different%20addresses%2C%20the%20shopper%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwo-store%20orders%20are%20even%20worse%20because%20it's%20like%20one%20store%20in%20Queens%2C%20the%20other%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20shopper%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThey%20really%20don't%20understand%20the%20distance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrders%20also%20get%20bundled%20together%20on%20restaurant%20delivery%20apps%20such%20as%20DoorDash%20and%20Uber%20Eats.%20Earnings%20aside%2C%20those%20batches%20often%20present%20another%20challenge%20for%20gig%20workers%3A%20Getting%20food%20to%20customers%20before%20it%20gets%20cold%20%E2%80%94%20or%20hot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20DoorDash%20customer%20expressed%20frustration%20that%20they%20were%20the%20third%20stop%20for%20the%20Dasher%20delivering%20their%20order%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Fdoordash%2Fcomments%2F13kezqx%2Fdouble_dashing_is_really_annoying_for_customers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20Reddit%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20picked%20my%20food%20up%20from%20the%20restaurant%20that%20is%207%20minutes%20away%2C%20but%20he%20has%20two%20other%20stops%20in%20the%20opposite%20directions%20before%20he%20gets%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20poster%20wrote%20of%20the%20delivery%20worker.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20ordered%20ice%20cream%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20your%20food%20is%20unacceptable%20when%20you%20receive%20it%2C%20(especially%20the%20ice%20cream)%2C%20you%20should%20complain%20to%20DoorDash%20that%20your%20food%20is%20ruined%20because%20your%20Dasher%20was%20on%20a%20triple%20stacked%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20commenter%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20for%20Instacart%2C%20Spark%2C%20or%20another%20delivery%20service%20and%20have%20a%20story%20idea%20to%20share%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20abitter%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-instacart-walmart-spark-gig-workers-hate-bundled-batch-orders-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705917961000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a9664adcdb354a9858a610%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-instacart-walmart-spark-gig-workers-hate-bundled-batch-orders-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bundling%20orders%20weighs%20on%20gig%20workers'%20earnings%20and%20frustrates%20some%20customers%20on%20platforms%20like%20Walmart's%20Spark.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abitter%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Bitter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2