f-l-k-advani%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20was%20founded%20in%201980%20and%20Advani%20assumed%20leadership%20of%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%20in%201984%20before%20becoming%20party%20president%20in%201986.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201989%2C%20the%20BJP%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpast-continuous-the-birth-of-the-ram-mandir-agitation%5C%22%3E%C2%A0announced%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20Ram%20temple%20on%20the%20land%20where%20they%20believed%20Lord%20Ram%20was%20born%20%E2%80%93%20and%20where%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20had%20stood%20for%20over%20400%20years%20%E2%80%93%20was%20its%20key%20political%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20autumn%20of%201990%2C%20Advani%20launched%20a%C2%A0%3Cem%3Erath%20yatra%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0from%20Somnath%20to%20Ayodhya%2C%20the%20purpose%20of%20which%20was%20to%20stir%20up%20support%20for%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20Ram%20temple%20at%20the%20spot%20where%20the%20mosque%20stood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Shiv%20temple%20had%20stood%20in%20Somnath%20since%20at%20least%20the%206th%C2%A0%C2%A0century%20CE.%20It%20was%20demolished%20and%20reconstructed%20several%20times%20over%20the%20centuries.%20The%20last%20demolition%20came%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20Mughal%20emperor%20Aurangzeb%20in%201665.%C2%A0It%20lay%20in%20ruins%20until%201950%20when%20its%20reconstruction%20began%20under%20the%20prime%20ministership%20of%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvani%E2%80%99s%20choice%20of%20beginning%20the%20yatra%20at%20Somnath%20and%20ending%20in%20Ayodhya%20thus%20had%20a%20very%20powerful%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fgurusmarana.ihrd.ac.in%2Ffiles%2Freligioussymbolsandpoliticalmobilisation_689.pdf%5C%22%3E%C2%A0symbolic%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0value%20of%20%E2%80%98reclaiming%E2%80%99%20the%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20as%20was%20done%20in%20Somnath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20wrote%20in%20his%202008%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcourtneylaportecarm.files.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F05%2Fmy-country-my-life-by-lk-advani-foreward-by-atal-bihari-vajpayee.pdf%5C%22%3Ebook%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3EMy%20Country%20My%20Life%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20choice%20of%20Somnath%20as%20the%20starting%20point%20of%20the%C2%A0%3Ci%3Eyatra%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0had%20a%20powerful%20symbolic%20value%2C%20made%20evident%20by%20repeated%20references%20to%20it%20as%20the%20target%20of%20Muslim%20tyranny%20against%20the%20Hindus%E2%80%A6The%20intention%20was%20to%20contextualise%20Ayodhya%20in%20the%20historical%20lineage%20of%20Muslim%20aggression%20and%20then%20to%20seek%20legitimacy%20for%20Mandir%20movement%20by%20drawing%20a%20parallel.%20The%20parallel%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%20drew%20was%20with%20the%20reconstruction%20of%20the%20Somnath%20temple.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvani%E2%80%99s%20rath%20yatra%20made%20it%20abundantly%20clear%20that%20he%20was%20not%20carrying%20a%20message%20of%20peace.%20Pictures%20of%20him%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fgurusmarana.ihrd.ac.in%2Ffiles%2Freligioussymbolsandpoliticalmobilisation_689.pdf%5C%22%3E%C2%A0carrying%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0a%C2%A0%3Cem%3Etrishul%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20an%20axe%2C%20a%20sword%20and%20a%20bow%20and%20arrow%20also%20emerged.%20Workers%20of%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%20and%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20pasted%20posters%20along%20the%20route%20of%20the%20yatra%20of%20the%20proposed%20temple%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fgurusmarana.ihrd.ac.in%2Ffiles%2Freligioussymbolsandpoliticalmobilisation_689.pdf%5C%22%3Etreachery%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20course%20of%20the%20yatra%20there%20was%20large%20scale%20violence%2C%20rioting%20and%20killings.%20Advani%20and%20his%20associates%20were%20finally%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Flalu-yadav-on-why-and-how-he-arrested-lk-advani-on-october-23-1990-1784734%5C%22%3E%C2%A0stopped%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20arrested%20by%20the%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav-led%20Bihar%20government%20in%20Samastipur%20in%20October%201990.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20the%20arrest%20of%20Advani%2C%20thousands%20of%C2%A0%3Ci%3Ekar%20sevaks%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0managed%20to%20reach%20Ayodhya%20where%2020%20of%20them%20were%20killed%20after%20a%20clash%20with%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20on%20December%206%2C%201992%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20was%20demolished%20by%20a%20mob%20of%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ekar%20sevaks%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0led%20by%20a%20coterie%20of%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20who%20in%20turn%20were%20led%20by%20Advani.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705915585000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fl-k-advani-who-led-ram-janmabhoomi-movement-skips-temple-consecration-citing-extreme-cold%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmbhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20had%20reportedly%20told%20him%20and%20his%20colleague%2C%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%2C%20not%20to%20attend%20the%20January%2022%20ceremony.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fl-k-advani-who-led-ram-janmabhoomi-movement-skips-temple-consecration-citing-extreme-cold%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BRam%20Lalla%20Will%20No%20Longer%20Live%20In%20A%20Tent%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi%20After%20Temple%20Ceremony%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%2C%20in%20a%20heartfelt%20speech%2C%20said%20that%20he%20is%20overjoyed%20that%20Lord%20Ram%20will%20no%20longer%20reside%20in%20a%20tent.%20PM%20Modi%20said%20that%20his%20%26quot%3Bthroat%20is%20choked%20and%20body%20is%20still%20shaking%26quot%3B%20as%20he%20speaks%20about%20the%20moment%20when%20the%20Ram%20idol%20was%20consecrated%20in%20the%20Ram%20Temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHere%20are%20PM%20Modi's%20top%20quotes%20from%20his%20address%20after%20Ram%20Temple%20'pran%20pratishtha'%20ceremony%20in%20Ayodhya%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EToday%2C%20our%20Ram%20has%20arrived%2C%20after%20generations%20of%20wait.%20On%20this%20auspicious%20occasion%2C%20congratulations%20to%20everyone.%20There's%20so%20much%20to%20tell%20but%2C%20but%20there's%20a%20lump%20in%20my%20throat.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERam%20Lalla%20will%20not%20stay%20in%20a%20tent.%20He%20will%20now%20stay%20in%20the%20magnificent%20temple.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJan%2022%2C%202024%20is%20not%20merely%20a%20date%20but%20marks%20advent%20of%20a%20new%20era.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20legal%20battle%20over%20the%20existence%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20went%20on%20for%20decades.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20express%20my%20gratitude%20to%20the%20judiciary%20of%20India%20for%20doing%20justice.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERam%20is%20mentioned%20in%20the%20first%20verse%20in%20our%20Constitution%2C%20yet%20it%20took%20so%20many%20decades%20for%20this%20to%20happen.%20That%20Constitutional%20finally%20holds%20true%20to%20its%20mention.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EToday%2C%20I%20also%20apologise%20to%20Lord%20Shri%20Ram.%20There%20must%20be%20something%20lacking%20in%20our%20effort%2C%20sacrifice%20and%20penance%20that%20we%20could%20not%20do%20this%20work%20for%20so%20many%20centuries.%20Today%20the%20work%20has%20been%20completed.%20I%20believe%20that%20Lord%20Shri%20Ram%20will%20definitely%20forgive%20us%20today.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI%20got%20the%20opportunity%20to%20travel%20from%20Sagar%20to%20Saryu.%20From%20Sagar%20to%20Saryu%2C%20the%20same%20festive%20spirit%20of%20Ram's%20name%20is%20visible%20everywhere.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERam%20is%20not%20fire%2C%20Ram%20is%20energy.%20Ram%20is%20not%20a%20dispute%2C%20Ram%20is%20the%20solution.%20Ram%20is%20not%20just%20ours%2C%20Ram%20is%20everyone's.%20Ram%20is%20not%20current%2C%20Ram%20is%20eternal.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20