%20in%20the%20home%20of%20their%20son%2C%20their%20own%20home%20yet%20to%20be%20rebuilt.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20four%20children%20who%20are%20thankfully%20all%20independent.%20If%20they%20were%20still%20in%20school%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20would%20be%20actually%20homeless%20because%20we%E2%80%99d%20have%20nowhere%20to%20live.%20But%20there%20are%20hundreds%20of%20such%20shopkeepers%20in%20this%20area%2C%20in%20Janoura%2C%20Ramnagar%20and%20so%20many%20other%20localities%20who%E2%80%99ve%20lost%20their%20homes%20or%20are%20now%20living%20on%20rent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22122845%2FSG1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22936%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22122845%2FSG1.jpg%20936w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22122845%2FSG1-300x225.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693961%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22702%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERakesh%20Kumar%20Gupta%20stands%20outside%20the%20remains%20of%20his%20three-storey%20shop%20and%20residence%2C%20yet%20to%20be%20rebuilt%20even%20a%20year%20since%20it%20was%20demolished.%20Photo%3A%20Sabah%20Gurmat%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20advent%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20has%20given%20the%20entire%20town%20a%20facelift%2C%20with%20the%20building%20and%20widening%20of%20roads%2C%20a%20revamped%20drainage%20system%20and%20railway%20station%2C%20and%20an%20airport.%20These%20changes%20are%20also%20ushering%20in%20a%20boom%20in%20property%20prices%20and%20real%20estate%20deals%2C%20along%20with%20hotel%20owners%20and%20leading%20corporate%20houses%20investing%20in%20this%20new%20temple%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20despite%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Flucknow%2Fcentralised-monitoring-of-projects-worth-over-rs-30k-crore-in-ayodhya%2Farticleshow%2F97036652.cms%5C%22%3Ewhopping%20Rs%2030%2C000%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20spent%20on%20this%20%E2%80%98new%20Ayodhya%E2%80%99%2C%20locals%20like%20Gupta%20are%20now%20paying%20the%20price%20of%20this%20development.%20Gupta%2C%20who%20built%20his%20three-storey%20residence%20in%201998%2C%20estimates%20the%20total%20value%20of%20his%20home%20and%20the%20land%20at%20%E2%80%9CRs%2080%20lakh%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20claims%20that%20authorities%20compensated%20him%20with%20a%20paltry%20Rs%209%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20just%20gave%20us%20compensation%20for%20the%20bricks%2C%20not%20for%20the%20land%20which%20the%20government%20claims%20is%20theirs.%20I%20see%20no%20hope%20of%20getting%20more%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20over%20a%20year%20now.%20They%20also%20said%20they%E2%80%99d%20widen%20the%20road%20by%2010%20metres%2C%20but%20actually%20took%20away%2012%20metres%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20despondently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20shops%20down%20the%20same%20road%20in%20Niyawan%20is%20Satyaprakash%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20small%20storefront.%20The%2045%20year%20old%20also%20owned%20a%20three-storey%20home%2C%20with%20the%20ground%20floor%20serving%20as%20his%20shop%20and%20workplace%2C%20but%20the%20home%20whose%20value%20he%20estimates%20at%20over%20Rs%2040%20lakh%20was%20compensated%20with%20just%20Rs%209%20lakh.%20Even%20as%20he%20used%20the%20compensation%20amount%20to%20rebuild%20his%20shop%2C%20he%20now%20lives%20on%20rent%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20three%20children%2C%20owing%20to%20the%20inability%20to%20rebuild%20the%20upper%20floors%20that%20once%20used%20to%20be%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20the%20only%20earning%20member%20in%20the%20family.%20Ever%20since%20the%20demolition%2C%20we%20haven%E2%80%99t%20had%20the%20resources%20to%20rebuild%20this%20entirely%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20rent%20a%20place%20for%20us%20to%20live.%20For%2010%20months%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20this%20shop%2C%20I%20drove%20an%20e-rickshaw%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%20and%20only%20got%20back%20to%20this%20now%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said%20wearily.%20Satprakash%E2%80%99s%20three%20children%20are%20in%20school%20and%20college%2C%20with%20his%20eldest%20son%20having%20to%20stop%20his%20MA%20degree%2C%20because%20he%20%E2%80%9Cdid%20not%20have%20the%20money%20to%20fill%20his%20fees%E2%80%9D.%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20364px)%2085vw%2C%20364px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22124431%2FSG2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22364%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22124431%2FSG2.jpg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22124431%2FSG2-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22124431%2FSG2-768x1024.jpg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693962%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22485%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESatyaprakash%20Gupta%20sits%20next%20to%20his%20tea%20kiosk%20in%20the%20newly-constructed%20kirana%20shop%20of%20a%20single%20storey%2C%20where%20once%20a%20three-storey%20shop%20as%20well%20as%20his%20family%20home%20existed.%20Photo%3A%20Sabah%20Gurmat%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20construction%20and%20painting%20are%20still%20ongoing%20in%20Ayodhya%E2%80%99s%20three%20main%20roads%20now%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Path%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Path%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Bhakti%20Path%E2%80%99%2C%20an%20estimate%20of%20between%204%2C000%20and%204%2C500%20shops%20and%20homes%20have%20been%20broken%20down%20or%20displaced%2C%20according%20to%20Nand%20Kumar%20Gupta%20who%20heads%20the%20Ayodhya%20Udyog%20Vyapar%20Mandal%20traders%E2%80%99%20union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Jalpa%2C%20women%20like%20Sumitra%20Devi%20claimed%20to%20have%20%E2%80%9Cprotested%20at%20first%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20have%20now%20been%20silenced%20into%20submission.%20Like%20Rakesh%20and%20Satya%20Prakash%20Gupta%2C%20she%20too%20owned%20a%20home%20and%20shop%20selling%20general%20supplies%2C%20only%20to%20see%20it%20razed.%20When%20contacted%2C%20the%20office%20of%20Ayodhya%20Development%20Authority%E2%80%99s%20chairman%20Vishal%20Singh%20said%20that%20questions%20of%20compensation%20and%20road-building%20were%20under%20the%20district%20magistrate%20and%20PWD%20department%E2%80%99s%20office.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20them%20for%20a%20comment%20and%20this%20story%20shall%20be%20updated%20when%20they%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFor%20Muslim-owned%20businesses%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20economic%20loss%20and%20damages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20lack%20of%20fair%20compensation%20has%20led%20to%20a%20sense%20of%20disillusionment%2C%20many%20shop%20owners%20like%20the%20Guptas%20continued%20to%20echo%20the%20belief%20that%20the%20temple%20would%20bring%20in%20an%20influx%20of%20religious%20tourism%20and%20cash%20flow.%20Despite%20his%20own%20resentment%20at%20the%20loss%20of%20his%20home%20and%20shop%2C%20Rakesh%20Kumar%20Gupta%20expressed%20enthusiasm%20for%20the%20Ram%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20Hindus%2C%20there%20is%20no%20question%20about%20our%20beliefs%20in%20the%20Ram%20temple%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20was%20a%20child%20who%20witnessed%20firsthand%20when%20violence%20broke%20out%20as%20karsevaks%20demolished%20the%20Babri%20mosque%20on%20December%206%2C%201992.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20was%20bound%20to%20happen%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20but%20refused%20to%20comment%20on%20whether%20he%20endorsed%20the%20violence%20that%20ensued.%20To%20those%20like%20him%2C%20the%20temple%20itself%20feels%20like%20a%20matter%20of%20personal%20faith%20and%20belief%20for%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20separate%20from%20their%20scrambling%20to%20save%20their%20demolished%20homes%20and%20businesses%20destroyed%20under%20the%20proposed%20development%20plan%20for%20the%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20others%20are%20not%20so%20sure%2C%20with%20Muslim-owned%20businesses%20having%20incurred%20losses%20not%20only%20in%20the%20process%20of%20construction%20work%2C%20but%20also%20as%20the%20promise%20of%20a%20temple%20town%20brings%20with%20it%20the%20exclusion%20of%20certain%20professions%20and%20communities.%20Virtually%20every%20shop%20in%20Ayodhya%E2%80%99s%20Bakra%20Mandi%20locality%20has%20been%20shut%20for%20the%20past%20week%2C%20with%20butchers%20from%20the%20area%20claiming%20that%20supplies%20that%20came%20from%20Bareilly%20have%20stopped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20no%20official%20notice%20or%20orders%2C%20we%20ourselves%20have%20stopped%20work%20for%20this%20week%20because%20devotees%20from%20all%20over%20India%20will%20be%20coming%20here%2C%20and%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20offend%20anyone%20in%20a%20way%20that%E2%80%99ll%20cause%20harm%20to%20our%20shops%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Farid%20Qureshi%2C%20who%20emphasised%20that%20the%20decision%20was%20taken%20of%20their%20own%20accord.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20meanwhile%20issued%20orders%20for%20the%20closure%20of%20all%20meat%20shops%20in%20the%20state%20on%20January%2022.%20Chief%20secretary%20D.S.%20Mishra%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Flucknow%2Fclosure-of-meat-shops-on-consecration-day-in-uttar-pradesh%2Farticleshow%2F106971537.cms%5C%22%3Ereportedly%3C%2Fa%3E%20directed%20all%20district%20magistrates%20to%20order%20meat%20and%20alcohol%20shops%20to%20remain%20shut%20for%20the%20day.%20While%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Flucknow%2Fmeat-liquor-should-not-be-allowed-in-ayodhya-cm-yogi-8663441%2F%5C%22%3Erepeatedly%20emphasised%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20past%20that%20the%20sale%20of%20meat%20and%20liquor%20will%20be%20banned%20for%20good%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Edharamnagri%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20of%20Ayodhya%2C%20so%20far%20there%20has%20been%20no%20official%20order%20to%20that%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20been%20a%20prohibition%20on%20selling%20non-veg%20and%20alcohol%20for%20the%204-5%20km%20radius%20around%20the%20temple%2C%20this%20has%20been%20the%20case%20for%20decades%20even%20under%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20local%20butcher%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20start%20of%20notices%20and%20increase%20in%20talks%20with%20district%20administration%20that%20has%20many%20worried%20that%20this%20prohibition%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20expanded%20to%2015%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammad%20Irfan%2C%20a%20meat-supplier%20and%20activist%20affiliated%20to%20the%20Tanzimul%20Quraish%20union%20of%20meat-sellers%2C%20said%20that%20as%20of%20now%2C%20the%20Food%20Security%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20department%20had%20sent%20notice%20regarding%20a%20ban%20on%20the%20sale%20of%20freshly%20cut%20meat%20in%20the%20open.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20told%20not%20to%20cut%20meat%20in%20the%20open%20on%20the%20roads%20since%20it%20is%20a%20holy%20town%2C%20but%20to%20instead%20sell%20packaged%20frozen%20meat.%20There%20is%20no%20ban%20on%20meat%20as%20such%20yet%2C%20but%20we%20do%20not%20know%20what%E2%80%99ll%20happen%20ultimately.%20It%E2%80%99s%20all%20going%20to%20become%20clear%20after%20the%2022nd%20of%20January%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20409px)%2085vw%2C%20409px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22125928%2FSG3.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22409%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22125928%2FSG3.jpg%20912w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22125928%2FSG3-228x300.jpg%20228w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22125928%2FSG3-778x1024.jpg%20778w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693963%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22538%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20photo%20of%20the%20latest%20notice%20issued%20regarding%20guidelines%20for%20the%20sale%20of%20meat%2C%20even%20as%20no%20official%20ban%20exists.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20no%20official%20ban%2C%20an%20estimated%20150%20to%20175%20butchers%20and%20shops%20have%20been%20hit%20by%20the%20FSDA%20norms.%20Irfan%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20decision%20could%20affect%20the%20livelihood%20of%20more%20than%20500%20families%2C%20especially%20causing%20job%20losses%20to%20those%20establishments%20with%20%E2%80%9C3-4%20extra%20hands%20working%20in%20each%20shop%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Niyawan%2C%20Faizan%20Qureshi%2C%20who%20continues%20to%20operate%20his%20shop%20and%20sell%20freshly%20cut%20meat%20for%20now%2C%20expressed%20concern%20that%20his%20employees%20would%20lose%20out.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20say%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20holy%20place%2C%20so%20we%20should%20respect%20sentiments%20by%20not%20cutting%20or%20displaying%20meat%20in%20the%20open.%20I%20understand%20that%20for%20the%20area%20near%20the%20temple%2C%20but%20how%20can%20they%20extend%20this%20for%20up%20to%2015%20km%3F%20Even%20if%20I%20can%20afford%20to%20switch%20to%20prepackaged%20and%20frozen%20meat%2C%20then%20I%20will%20need%20less%20manpower%20and%20will%20have%20to%20fire%20the%20other%20staff%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQureshi%20also%20believes%20that%20such%20a%20ban%2C%20if%20implemented%2C%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20sustain%20in%20correlation%20with%20the%20rise%20in%20hotels%20and%20real%20estate%20ventures.%20With%20hotel%20chains%20like%20the%20Radisson%2C%20Oberoi%20and%20Taj%20groups%20having%20already%20begun%20or%20lining%20up%20to%20set%20up%20shop%20in%20the%20town%2C%20the%20young%20meat%20seller%20still%20holds%20hope%20that%20ongoing%20talks%20with%20district%20authorities%20could%20see%20fruition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20the%20Muslim-dominated%20meat%20trade%20which%20could%20see%20prospects%20dim%2C%20as%20a%20climate%20of%20fear%20and%20chilling%20effect%20looms%20over%20the%20nearly%20four%20lakh%20Muslims%20in%20the%20region%20even%20otherwise.%20In%20Asharfi%20Bhavan%2C%20a%20neighbourhood%20located%20close%20to%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20complex%2C%20rumours%20are%20abuzz%20that%20the%20proximity%20to%20the%20temple%20can%20cause%20physical%20and%20communal%20tensions%20to%20simmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20area%20was%20targeted%20in%201992%2C%20there%20are%20many%20Muslim%20families%20living%20here.%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20born%20back%20then%2C%20but%20me%20and%20my%20cousins%20are%20worried%20that%20devotees%20from%20outside%20can%20come%20and%20try%20provoking%20people%20here%20on%20purpose%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%2024-year-old%20Mohammad%20Aamir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERising%20fears%20and%20forced%20uniformity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20tensions%20heighten%20across%20the%20town%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fnational%2Fmuslims-in-ayodhya-seek-increased-police-protection-in-neighbourhoods-ahead-of-jan-22-news-343693%5C%22%3Ereports%20suggest%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20residents%20have%20demanded%20police%20protection%20and%20additional%20security%20measures%20in%20%E2%80%9Csensitive%E2%80%9D%20neighbourhoods%20like%20Verma%20Colony%2C%20Tedhi%20Bazar%20and%20Baheliya%20Tola%20neighbourhoods%20beside%20the%20AC%20Masjid%20and%20the%20Asharfi%20Bhawan%20water%20tank%2C%20among%20other%20places%2C%20all%20of%20which%20saw%20communal%20violence%20in%201992%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20arterial%20roads%20as%20well%2C%20every%20shop%E2%80%99s%20shutter%20has%20been%20painted%20a%20uniform%20set%20of%20Hindu%20religious%20symbols%20and%20iconography%20from%20the%20Ramayana.%20MH%2C%20a%20Muslim%20shopkeeper%20who%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20disclose%20his%20name%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20he%20was%20given%20a%20list%20of%20%E2%80%9Cfive%20to%20six%20options%20of%20symbols%20to%20choose%20from%2C%20including%20a%20mace%2C%20shankh%20(conch)%2C%20swastika%2C%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram%20slogan%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Edamru%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20by%20the%20contractors%20who%20had%20come%20to%20paint.%20He%20chose%20a%20symbol%20of%20the%20mace%2C%20with%20another%20Muslim%20shopowner%20in%20the%20lane%20opting%20for%20a%20damru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20595px)%2085vw%2C%20595px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22131309%2FSG4.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22595%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22131309%2FSG4.jpg%20936w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22131309%2FSG4-300x269.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693964%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAcross%20Ayodhya%E2%80%99s%20arterial%20roads%2C%20the%20shutters%20of%20every%20shop%20bears%20religious%20iconography%20from%20the%20Ramayana%2C%20with%20a%20uniformly%20planned%20look.%20Photo%3A%20Sabah%20Gurmat%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20several%20across%20the%20country%20watch%20the%20consecration%20and%20its%20aftermath%20with%20bated%20breath%2C%20these%20spatial%20changes%20and%20socio-economic%20losses%20experienced%20by%20Ayodhya%E2%