ason%20for%20the%20termination%20in%20a%20letter%20sent%20to%20ZEEL%20today.%20The%20merger%2C%20which%20was%20announced%20more%20than%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20hit%20an%20impasse%20over%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20merged%20company%2C%20amid%20a%20market%20regulator%20probe%20into%20Zee%20CEO%20Punit%20Goenka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZEEL%20in%20an%20exchange%20filing%20responded%20to%20the%20Sony%20notice%2C%20which%20also%20sought%20%2490%20million%20on%20account%20of%20alleged%20breaches%20by%20ZEEL%20of%20the%20merger%20cooperation%20agree%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BZEEL%20categorically%20denies%20all%20the%20assertions%20raised%20by%20Culver%20Max%20and%20BEPL%20on%20the%20alleged%20breaches%20under%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20MCA%2C%20including%20their%20claims%20for%20the%20termination%20fee%2C%26quot%3B%20ZEEL%20said%20in%20the%20filing%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECulver%20Max%20Entertainment%20Pvt%20Ltd%20was%20earlier%20known%20as%20Sony%20Pictures%20Networks%20India%2C%20and%20BEPL%20is%20short%20for%20Bangla%20Entertainment%20Pvt%20Ltd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20ZEEL%20also%20held%20several%20deliberations%20and%20good%20faith%20negotiations%20with%20Culver%20Max%20and%20BEPL%2C%20with%20a%20view%20to%20consider%20an%20extension%20of%20the%20merger%20completion%20timeline%2C%20that%20did%20not%20materialise%2C%26quot%3B%20ZEEL%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZEEL%20said%20its%20managing%20director%20and%20CEO%20Punit%20Goenka%20was%20agreeable%20to%20step%20down%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20merger%20and%20proposals%20in%20this%20regard%20were%20discussed%2C%20including%20for%20appointment%20of%20a%20director%20on%20the%20board%20of%20the%20merged%20company%2C%20protections%20for%20conduct%20of%20pending%20investigations%20and%20legal%20proceedings%20in%20the%20best%20interest%20of%20ZEEL's%20directors%20and%20shareholders%20and%20the%20consequent%20modifications%20to%20the%20scheme%20to%20incorporate%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BZEEL's%20board%20of%20directors%20is%20evaluating%20all%20the%20available%20options.%20Basis%20the%20guidance%20received%20from%20the%20board%2C%20ZEEL%20will%20take%20steps%20to%20protect%20the%20long-term%20interests%20of%20all%20its%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20by%20taking%20appropriate%20legal%20action%20and%20contesting%20Culver%20Max%20and%20BEPL's%20claims%20in%20the%20arbitration%20proceedings%2C%26quot%3B%20ZEEL%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZEEL%20chairman%20R%20Gopalan%20in%20the%20filing%20said%20they%20are%20evaluating%20the%20next%20steps%20and%20considering%20the%20appropriate%20course%20of%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20The%20board%20has%20noted%20that%20the%20company%20took%20all%20the%20required%20steps%20in%20the%20course%20of%20its%20integration%20journey%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20scheme%20is%20implemented%20at%20the%20earliest.%20That%20said%2C%20the%20Board%20would%20like%20to%20assure%20its%20stakeholders%20that%20the%20company%20will%20take%20all%20the%20necessary%20actions%2C%20in%20the%20best%20interest%20of%20all%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20by%20taking%20appropriate%20legal%20action%20and%20contesting%20Culver%20Max%20and%20BEPL's%20claims%20in%20the%20arbitration%20proceedings%2C%26quot%3B%20R%20Gopalan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705911000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F85na1jh8_zee-sony_625x300_10_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-sony-notice-zee-denies-alleged-breach-of-merger-terms-4909485%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22ZEE%20Entertainment%20Enterprises%20Ltd%20(ZEEL)%20held%20a%20board%20meeting%20today%20to%20take%20note%20of%20the%20merger%20termination%20notice%20sent%20by%20Japan's%20Sony%20Group%20Corp.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-sony-notice-zee-denies-alleged-breach-of-merger-terms-4909485%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-sony-notice-zee-denies-alleged-breach-of-merger-terms-4909485%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-sony-notice-zee-denies-alleged-breach-of-merger-terms-4909485%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2225%20experts%20calculated%20the%20scenarios%20they%20think%20could%20play%20out%20in%20the%20US-China%20relationship.%20All%20the%20results%20are%20bleak.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20greets%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20before%20a%20meeting%20during%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20Economic%20Cooperation%20(APEC)%20Leaders'%20week%20in%20Woodside%2C%20California%20on%20November%2015%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ae08fd617029e90a5ee023%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221856%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20greets%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20before%20a%20meeting%20during%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20Economic%20Cooperation%20(APEC)%20Leaders'%20week%20in%20Woodside%2C%20California%20on%20November%2015%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EBRENDAN%20SMIALOWSKI%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20new%20analysis%20compiling%2025%20experts'%20thoughts%20on%20US-China%20relations%20forecasts%20a%20bleak%20outlook.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20summarized%20their%20theories%20into%20four%20scenarios.%20None%20of%20them%20were%20positive.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20bottom%20line%20was%20clear%3A%20The%20upbeat%20attitude%20of%C2%A0%26quot%3Bshared%20growth%26quot%3B%20in%20the%201980s%20isn't%20coming%20back.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20future%20of%20US-China%20relations%20looks%20grim%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20report%20by%20a%20group%20of%2025%20experts%20on%20both%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20compiled%20theories%20from%20former%20senior%20Obama%20and%20Trump%20administration%20officials%2C%20retired%20researchers%20from%20the%20Chinese%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%2C%20and%20academics%20on%20both%20sides%2C%20said%20non-profit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fuschinascenarios.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPax%20Sapiens%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20organized%20the%20collaboration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20summary%20of%20their%20opinions%20outlined%20four%20major%20plausible%20scenarios%20that%20could%20unfold%20by%202035%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E1)%20All-out%20war%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E2)%20Both%20countries%20rule%20separate%20blocs%20of%20the%20world%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E3)%20A%20refusal%20from%20both%20parties%20to%20cooperate%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E4)%20Both%20countries%20communicate%20regularly%20while%20their%20economies%20slowly%20decouple%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20none%20of%20these%20scenarios%20include%20an%20outcome%20many%20investors%20and%20business%20leaders%20still%20hope%20for%20%E2%80%94%20a%20dream%20of%20shared%20growth%20that%20seemed%20possible%20amid%20thawing%20relations%20in%20the%20post-Cold%20War%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20different%20reality%20now%20exists%20compared%20to%20the%201980s%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20with%20the%20US%20seeing%20China%20as%20a%20threat%20that%20breaks%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20world%20order%20and%20Beijing%20viewing%20Washington%20as%20trying%20to%20stifle%20its%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObservers%20in%20both%20countries%20predict%20near-term%20economic%20difficulties%20in%20the%20other%2C%20and%20neither%20feels%20the%20other%20appreciates%20its%20history%20or%20values%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20sides%20think%20their%20military%20actions%20are%20defensive%2C%20while%20the%20other's%20is%20provocative%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20every%20expert%20agreed%20on%20all%20the%20details%20in%20each%20scenario%2C%20but%20the%20analysis%20represents%20a%20loose%20consensus%20of%20their%20thoughts%2C%20Pax%20Sapiens%20said%20in%20the%20full%20report%20released%20last%20week%2C%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1)%20War%20over%20Taiwan%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20war%20were%20to%20happen%2C%20the%20report%20posits%20that%20it%20may%20break%20out%20in%20the%20early%202030s%20over%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experts%20listed%20a%20timeline%20of%20specific%20events%20that%20are%20purely%20theoretical%2C%20but%20cover%20flashpoints%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20direct%20hostilities%20when%20combined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20lawmakers%20call%20for%20bans%20against%20Chinese%20students%2C%20Taiwan%20starts%20to%20assert%20independence%2C%20China%20encircles%20the%20island%2C%20and%20the%20Pentagon%20announces%20it%20will%20defend%20Taipei%2C%20the%20analysis%20said.%20And%20US%20scientists%20might%20find%20a%20mysterious%20avian%20flu%20in%20China%2C%20while%20China%20detains%20five%20Americans%20on%20accusations%20that%20they%20broke%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20a%20case%20of%20a%20single%20escalatory%20event%2C%20or%20a%20single%20crisis%20that%20spins%20out%20of%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20Conor%20Seyle%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20operations%20at%20Pax%20Sapiens%20and%20one%20of%20the%20analysis'%20organizers%2C%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDvoblmoQbzE%26t%3D407s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eat%20a%20briefing%20on%20Friday%20about%20the%20analysis.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20the%20war%20scenario%20is%20a%20scenario%20of%20increasing%20crises%20leading%20to%20increasing%20distrust%20in%20diplomatic%20solutions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20trust%20breaks%20down%2C%20a%20series%20of%20mishaps%20like%20US%20and%20Chinese%20navy%20ships%20colliding%20or%20clashing%2C%20would%20likely%20tip%20both%20countries%20into%20a%20full-scale%20war.%20The%20scenario%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20go%20so%20far%20as%20to%20predict%20nuclear%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2)%20A%20zero-sum%20bloc%20game%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOr%20US-China%20trade%20could%20fall%20to%20all-time%20lows%20by%20the%20late%202020s%2C%20with%20competition%20ramping%20up%20over%20AI%2C%20quantum%20computers%2C%20and%20other%20technology%2C%20the%20analysis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20both%20sides%20impose%20more%20export%20controls%20on%20each%20other%2C%20US%20allies%20in%20Europe%20and%20the%20Asia%20Pacific%20might%20band%20together%20with%20Washington%2C%20while%20BRICS%20%E2%80%94%20the%20bloc%20involving%20Brazil%2C%20Russia%2C%20India%2C%20China%2C%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20%E2%80%94%20develop%20their%20own%20separate%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BParallel%2C%20mutually%20firewalled%2C%20and%20incompatible%20technology%20regimes%20discourage%20and%2C%20in%20some%20instances%2C%20prevent%20communication%20across%20blocs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20theorized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProxy%20wars%20involving%20religious%20extremists%20or%20terrorists%20might%20become%20more%20frequent%2C%20while%20Latin%20America%20and%20Africa%20become%20divided%20over%20who%20they%20side%20with%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20positive%20element%20of%20this%20scenario%20is%20that%20green%20technology%20might%20flourish%20because%20of%20an%20urgent%20need%20for%20more%20energy%2C%20the%20analysis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20overall%2C%20the%20result%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bthe%20collapse%20of%20the%20WTO%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Ba%20negative%20drag%20on%20global%20GDP%20growth%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20zero-sum%20game%20between%20Washington%20and%20Beijing.%20The%20threat%20of%20war%20would%20also%20linger%20by%202035%2C%20the%20experts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E3)%20%26quot%3BLurch%20from%20crisis%20to%20crisis%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20possible%20that%20while%20no%20confrontation%20takes%20place%20by%202035%2C%20communication%20and%20cooperation%20between%20both%20countries%20could%20worsen%2C%20the%20analysis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20scenario%20predicts%20what%20would%20happen%20with%20two%20prerequisites%3A%20China%20solidifies%20its%20presence%20as%20a%20global%20trade%20power%2C%20enough%20for%20Europe%20to%20bolster%20economic%20ties%20with%20Beijing%2C%20and%20the%20US%20scales%20back%20visits%20to%20and%20aggressive%20support%20for%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20both%20countries%20will%20accuse%20each%20other%20of%20violating%20international%20trade%20rules%20%E2%80%94%20the%20US%20would%20say%20China%20uses%20state%20resources%20to%20create%20unfair%20market%20competition%2C%20while%20China%20would%20say%20the%20US%20does%20the%20same%20and%20holds%20itself%20to%20a%20double%20standard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeijing%20and%20Washington%20might%20manage%20to%20avoid%20war%20by%20showing%20baseline%20restraint%2C%20but%20nothing%20more%2C%20the%20analysis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20mutual%20agreements%20or%20guiding%20principles%20to%20shepherd%20their%20relations%2C%20the%20United%20States%20and%20China%20could%20%26quot%3Blurch%20from%20crisis%20to%20crisis%20with%20ad%20hoc%20responses%2C%20barely%20managing%20to%20forestall%20escalation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E4)%20Self-reliance%20and%20a%20modified%20status%20quo%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20sunniest%20of%20these%20scenarios%20is%20the%20idea%20that%20the%20US%20and%20China%20might%20slowly%20and%20calculatingly%20decouple%20their%20economies%20in%20a%20way%20that%20avoids%20misunderstanding%20or%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20analysis%20says%20that%20in%20this%20timeline%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20clear%20that%20the%20main%20tenets%20of%20the%20post-1980s%20US-China%20bilateral%20relationship%20have%20broken%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20nations%20may%20start%20to%20emphasize%20self-reliance%2C%20specifically%20building%20up%20their%20economies%20to%20function%20without%20the%20other%2C%20the%20analysis%20said.%20The%20winners%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20low-%20and%20middle-income%20countries%20in%20Latin%20America%2C%20Africa%2C%20and%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20with%20their%20raw%20materials%20and%20labor%20being%20coveted%20by%20either%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20in%20this%20scenario%2C%20the%20two%20countries%20maintain%20regular%20communication%20channels%20to%20avoid%20escalation%20whenever%20small%20crises%20take%20place%2C%20the%20analysis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaiwan%20would%20avoid%20declaring%20independence%2C%20while%20the%20US%20would%20stick%20to%20the%20One%20China%20Policy.%20China%20might%20start%20to%20think%20that%20if%20it%20could%20dominate%20global%20trade%2C%20Taipei%20would%20eventually%20ask%20to%20reunify.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20even%20with%20this%20hope%20for%20selective%20engagement%2C%20the%20US-China%20relationship%20remains%20vulnerable%20to%20political%20swings%20in%20both%20countries%20that%20could%20easily%20lead%20to%20rapid%20deterioration%20in%20relations%20and%20a%20dangerous%20escalation%20of%20tensions%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeyle%20emphasized%20that%20the%20analysis%20isn't%20presenting%20forecasts%2C%20but%20theoretical%20scenarios%20that%20hit%20areas%20of%20concern%20in%20broad%20strokes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20why%20it's%20narrative%20is%20because%20we%20are%20story-telling%20creatures%2C%26quot%3B%20Seyle%20said%20at%20the%20Friday%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20closing%20section%2C%20he%20and%20two%20of%20the%20report's%20organizers%20said%20they%20intended%20for%20the%20analysis%20to%20realistically%20%26quot%3Banticipate%20possible%20challenges%20the%20two%20countries%20might%20plausibly%20be%20facing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20organized%20this%20project%20at%20a%20time%20of%20general%20pessimism%20about%20the%20prospect%20of%20the%20current%20US-China%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Seyle%2C%20Ren%20Libo%20of%20the%20Chinese%20think%20tank%20Grandview%20Institute%2C%20and%20Adam%20Kahane%20of%20Massachusetts-based%20consultancy%20Reos%20Partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F25-experts-theorize-future-us-china-relations-war-economy-bleak-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705910998000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ae093c617029e90a5ee02b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F25-experts-theorize-future-us-china-relations-war-economy-bleak-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20experts%2C%20including%20former%20Trump%20and%20Obama%20officials%20and%20retired%20researchers%20in%20the%20PLA%2C%20posited%20four%20probable%20scenarios%2C%20none%20of%20which%20were%20positive.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A35%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F25-experts-theorize-future-us-china-relations-war-economy-bleak-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sony-Zee%20merger%3A%20ZEE%20promises%20legal%20action%20over%20termination%20notice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705910905000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2021-10%2F27%2Ffull%2F1635317871-3456.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsony-zee-merger-zee-promises-legal-action-over-termination-notice-124012200345_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Culver%20Max%20and%20BEPL%20sent%20a%20termination%20notice%20with%20a%20%2490%20million%20fee%20to%20ZEEL%20after%20Sony%20cancelled%20the%20merger%20deal%20valued%20at%20%2410%20billion%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsony-zee-merger-zee-promises-legal-action-over-termination-notice-124012200345_1.html%22