0Dev%20also%20cited%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20climate%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20day%20without%20elaborating%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20said%20it%20is%20as%20if%20we%20have%20returned%20to%20the%20Treta%20Yug%20%E2%80%93%20the%20second%20best%20of%20the%20four%20mythical%20slots%20of%20time%20observed%20in%20Hinduism.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20a%20nation%20put%20in%20so%20much%20effort%20over%20such%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time%20to%20get%20a%20temple%20in%20this%20manner%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Adityanath.%20He%20spoke%20of%20%E2%80%9Csacrifices%E2%80%9D%20Hindus%20have%20made%2C%20apparently%20coming%20together%20across%20caste%20and%20community%2C%20to%20make%20this%20temple%20a%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%E2%80%99s%20sacrifice%20has%20borne%20fruit%20because%20the%20temple%20was%20built%20exactly%20where%20we%20had%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20built%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%2C%20using%20the%20famous%20Hindi%20phrase%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EMandir%20wahi%20banayenge%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%E2%80%99%20which%20was%20popularised%20by%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%20destruction%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%201992%20and%20afterwards.%20He%20credited%20Modi%20with%20this%20becoming%20possible%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20with%20his%20election%20win%20in%202014%20that%20Hindus%20were%20able%20to%20achieve%20this%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20holy%20land%20will%20be%20the%20cultural%20capital%20of%20the%20world%2C%20Adityanath%20claimed.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20double%20engine%20government%20has%20made%20all%20dreams%20of%20Ayodhya%20real%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20listing%20all%20the%20avenues%20in%20which%20the%20Modi%20government%20at%20the%20Union%20and%20his%2C%20in%20the%20state%2C%20have%20apparently%20made%20the%20city%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERSS%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20al