deity%2C%20flanked%20by%20several%20saints%20in%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20of%20the%20temple.%20RSS%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20was%20also%20present.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2051-inch%20idol%2C%20carved%20out%20of%20black%20stone%20by%20Mysuru-based%20artist%20Arun%20Yogiraj%2C%20had%20been%20covered%20with%20a%20veil%20in%20the%20days%20leading%20up%20to%20today's%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ram%20Lalla%20idol%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%20of%20the%20new%20temple%20represents%20five-yea-old%20Ram.%20The%20first%20floor%20of%20the%20temple%2C%20which%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20built%2C%20will%20have%20the%20idol%20of%20Raja%20Ram%2C%20along%20with%20Sita%2C%20Laxman%20and%20Hanuman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20a%20photograph%20of%20the%20idol%20that%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20had%20sparked%20a%20row%2C%20with%20the%20chief%20priest%20of%20the%20temple%20demanding%20a%20probe%20into%20who%20circulated%20it.%20The%20photograph%2C%20the%20priest%20said%2C%20showed%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20idol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20eyes%20of%20Lord%20Ram's%20idol%20cannot%20be%20revealed%20before%20the%20'Pran%20Pratishtha'%20is%20completed.%20If%20the%20eyes%20can%20be%20seen%2C%20an%20investigation%20should%20be%20done%20on%20who%20revealed%20the%20eyes%20and%20how%20the%20pictures%20of%20the%20idol%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%26quot%3B%20chief%20priest%20Satyendra%20Das%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20galaxy%20of%20film%20stars%2C%20sportspersons%2C%20musicians%2C%20industrialists%20and%20other%20noted%20personalities%20have%20reached%20the%20holy%20town%20for%20the%20ground%20consecration%20ceremony.%20Over%2011%2C000%20invitations%20have%20been%20sent%20out%20to%20noted%20personalities.%20The%20Opposition%20has%20stayed%20away%20from%20the%20event.%20While%20some%20parties%20have%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20politicising%20the%20religious%20occasion%2C%20other%20Opposition%20leaders%20have%20said%20they%20would%20visit%20the%20temple%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705909080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F05hd5uj8_ram-lalla_625x300_22_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fram-lalla-idol-revealed-at-ayodhya-temple-adorned-in-gold-flowers-4909410%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Adorned%20with%20gold%20and%20flowers%2C%20the%2051-inch%20Ram%20Lalla%20idol%20was%20revealed%20today%20shortly%20before%20the%20grand%20'pran%20pratistha'%20ceremony%20at%20the%20Ayodhya%20temple%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fram-lalla-idol-revealed-at-ayodhya-temple-adorned-in-gold-flowers-4909410%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fram-lalla-idol-revealed-at-ayodhya-temple-adorned-in-gold-flowers-4909410%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fram-lalla-idol-revealed-at-ayodhya-temple-adorned-in-gold-flowers-4909410%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ananya%20wants%20to%20delete%20all%20her%20social%20media%20apps%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705908852000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107047526%2Cimgsize-23350.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fananya-panday-wants-to-delete-all-her-social-media-apps-but-just-cant-heres-why%2Farticleshow%2F107047603.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107047603.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EActress%20Ananya%20Panday%20expresses%20the%20desire%20to%20delete%20social%20media%20apps%20due%20to%20their%20negative%20impact%20on%20mental%20health%2C%20but%20finds%20it%20challenging.%20She%20discusses%20the%20struggle%20to%20take%20a%20break%20from%20constant%20connectivity%2C%20citing%20the%20juxtaposition%20of%20distressing%20news%20and%20lighthearted%20content.%20Ananya%20is%20set%20to%20appear%20in%20the%20OTT%20show%20%26quot%3BCall%20Me%20Bae%26quot%3B%20and%20Vikramaditya%20Motwane's%20film%20%26quot%3BControl.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fananya-panday-wants-to-delete-all-her-social-media-apps-but-just-cant-heres-why%2Farticleshow%2F107047603.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Here's%20when%20Apple%20may%20launch%20new%20iPad%2C%20MacBook%20Air%20in%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705908668000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107047488%2Cimgsize-245074.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fapple-to-launch-new-ipad-pro-ipad-and-macbook-air-in-2024%2Farticleshow%2F107047488.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22New%20models%20of%20iPad%20Air%2C%20iPad%20Pro%20and%20MacBook%20Air%20are%20expected%20quite%20soon%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Bloomberg.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Ram%20Rajya%20And%20Our%20Civilisational%20Reawakening%20-%20by%20R%20Jagannathan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20consecration%20of%20the%20Shri%20Ram%20Mandir%20is%20an%20epochal%20event%20in%20India's%20civilisational%20history%2C%20something%20that%20dwarfs%20the%20rebuilding%20of%20the%20Somnath%20temple%20in%20the%201950s%20and%201960s.%20When%20the%20Somnath%20temple%20was%20rebuilt%2C%20not%20only%20did%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20that%20time%20see%20it%20as%20something%20the%20state%20should%20not%20associate%20itself%20with%2C%20it%20also%20came%20in%20the%20immediate%20aftermath%20of%20our%20bloody%20partition.%20It%20was%20a%20time%20when%20our%20frightened%20minorities%20needed%20reassurance%2C%20and%20they%20got%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20not%20the%20case%20now%2C%20and%20a%20Hindu%20population%20that%20has%20lost%20touch%20with%20its%20culture%20and%20civilisational%20heritage%20over%20the%20last%20few%20decades%20is%20seeking%20to%20reconnect%20with%20the%20past.%20Hence%20the%20exuberance%20over%20the%2022%20January%20%3Cem%3Epran%20pratishtha%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20Shri%20Ram.%20This%20time%20the%20incumbent%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20at%20the%20very%20centre%20of%20this%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flip%20side%20of%20Indian%20secularism%20so%20far%20has%20been%20its%20one-sidedness.%20The%20majority%20community%20was%20effectively%20asked%20to%20play%20down%20its%20heritage%2C%20except%20for%20guilt-tripping%20it%20over%20the%20negative%20aspects%20like%20casteism.%20The%20Nehruvian-Left%20consensus%20was%20that%20India%20would%20be%20best%20served%20by%20a%20partly%20fictional%20history%20that%20talked%20little%20about%20the%20damage%20done%20to%20the%20Hindu%20psyche%20by%20several%20hundred%20years%20of%20Islamic%20iconoclasm.%20While%20Nehru's%20secularism%20was%20driven%20by%20his%20own%20deeply%20felt%20convictions%20against%20mixing%20politics%20with%20religion%2C%20his%20successors%20used%20secularism%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20court%20the%20minority%20bloc%20vote.%20And%20with%20the%20Hindu%20vote%20being%20divided%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20and%20many%20regional%20parties%20in%20states%2C%20could%20comfortably%20win%20elections%20by%20trampling%20on%20Hindu%20sensitivities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20happened%20in%20the%20decades%20after%20Nehru%20was%20a%20deracination%20of%20the%20average%20Hindu%2C%20who%20not%20only%20got%20alienated%20from%20his%20roots%2C%20but%20was%20additionally%20asked%20to%20view%20his%20religion%20only%20in%20negative%20terms%20-%20through%20the%20prism%20of%20casteism%20and%20the%20damage%20it%20did%20to%20social%20cohesion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20four%20decades%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20telecasting%20of%20the%20Ramayan%20and%20Mahabharat%20serials%20on%20Doordarshan%2C%20the%20sense%20of%20loss%20of%20our%20civilisational%20heritage%20deepened.%20This%20is%20what%20provided%20the%20emotive%20glue%20and%20mass%20awakening%20needed%20to%20convert%20a%20feeling%20of%20loss%20into%20a%20political%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20huge%20expressions%20of%20joy%20and%20assertiveness%20we%20see%20today%20are%20signs%20of%20a%20civilisational%20rebirth%20that%20cannot%20be%20denied.%20It%20is%20easy%20to%20dismiss%20this%20as%20just%20a%20RSS%2FBJP%20political%20event%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20but%20it%20would%20be%20churlish%20to%20assume%20that%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20could%20have%20been%20built%20without%20the%20political%20mobilisation%20that%20preceded%20it.%20Even%20the%20courts%2C%20while%20giving%20a%20verdict%20based%20on%20solid%20legal%20arguments%2C%20could%20not%20have%20failed%20to%20notice%20the%20underlying%20upsurge%20of%20feelings%20among%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rejuvenation%20of%20Ayodhya%2C%20and%20other%20pilgrimage%20sites%20in%20Kashi%2C%20Ujjain%2C%20Puri%20and%20Mathura%2C%20is%20to%20be%20celebrated%20for%20the%20simple%20reason%20that%20most%20of%20them%20are%20based%20in%20some%20of%20our%20poorer%20regions.%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20is%20at%20the%20epicentre%20of%20our%20cultural%20and%20religious%20past%2C%20with%20three%20of%20the%20holiest%20Hindu%20sites%20located%20there.%20The%20creation%20of%20a%20new%20religious%20hub%20around%20Ayodhya%2C%20Kashi%20and%20Prayagrag%20will%20complement%20the%20development%20of%20the%20western%20region%20that%20benefits%20from%20being%20part%20of%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR).%20Noida%20and%20its%20new%20airport%20will%20bring%20economic%20benefits%20of%20the%20kind%20that%20catapulted%20Haryana%20from%20a%20Bimaru%20state%20to%20one%20of%20its%20richest.%20While%20Western%20UP%20will%20benefit%20from%20its%20proximity%20to%20Delhi%2C%20eastern%20UP%20will%20rise%20on%20the%20shoulders%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20and%20the%20religious%20tourism%20that%20it%20fosters.%20If%20Mathura%20is%20rejuvenated%20like%20Ayodhya%2C%20Western%20UP%20will%20get%20three%20engines%20for%20growth%2C%20including%20its%20existing%20tourist%20draw%20of%20Agra's%20Taj%20Mahal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehru%20was%20wrong%20to%20assume%20that%20religion%20is%20the%20antithesis%20of%20modernity%20and%20development.%20Ayodhya%20will%20prove%20that%20over%20the%20next%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Shri%20Ram%20is%20not%20just%20a%20UP%20phenomenon.%20He%20is%20a%20national%20icon%2C%20as%20one%20can%20see%20from%20the%20celebrations%20now%20seen%20in%20almost%20every%20state%2C%20including%20the%20south.%20While%20religious%20developments%20in%20the%20south%20have%20been%20different%20from%20the%20north%2C%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20north%20and%20south%20have%20always%20been%20civilisationally%20joined%20at%20the%20hip.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20was%20Tamil%20kings%20of%20the%20Chola%20dynasty%20who%20took%20Hinduism%20to%20south-east%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20will%20say%20that%20Shri%20Ram%20was%20a%20%3Cem%3EMaryada%20Purushottam%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20he%20would%20not%20have%20wanted%20his%20temple%20built%20by%20excluding%20Muslims%20from%20being%20equal%20partners%20in%20nation-building.%20To%20be%20sure%2C%20reconciliation%20has%20to%20be%20a%20two-way%20process.%20One%20can%20only%20hope%20that%20a%20new%20truth%20and%20reconciliation%20process%20is%20initiated%20once%20the%20temple%20is%20open%20to%20all%20comers.%20Shri%20Ram's%20return%20to%20Ayodhya%20should%20mark%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20Hindu-Muslim%20relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20editorial%20director%2C%20Swarajya%20magazine)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ED