0a%20formerly%20mixed%20neighbourhood%20of%20Ahmedabad%2C%20which%20saw%20communal%20massacres%20a%20day%20after%20the%20Godhra%20train%20burning%20on%20February%2028%2C%202002%20and%20the%20brutal%20murder%20of%2096%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20being%20a%20survivor%2C%20Bano%20is%20also%20a%20witness%20of%20the%20Naroda%20Patiya%20massacre%20and%20had%20identified%20at%20least%20four%20rioters%20who%20killed%20and%20raped%20Muslims%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20witnesses%20like%20Bano%20were%20informed%20in%20December%202023%20that%20the%20police%20is%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fahmedabad%2F02-riots-guj-revokes-security-of-witnesses-former-judge%2Farticleshow%2F106359690.cms%5C%22%3Ewithdraw%3C%2Fa%3E%20their%20security%20cover.%20Many%20such%20witnesses%20were%20in%20the%20protected%20persons%20category%20since%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%2015%20years%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court-appointed%20special%20investigation%20team%20formed%20a%20witness%20protection%20cell%20for%20the%20complainants%2Fwitnesses%20of%20the%202002%20riots.%20The%20Gujarat%20government%20has%20now%20withdrawn%20security%20cover%20of%20various%20witnesses%2C%20lawyers%20of%20victims%20and%20even%20a%20judge%20who%20convicted%2032%20accused%20in%20the%20Naroda%20Patiya%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202009%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fheadlines-today-top-stories%2Fstory%2Fgujarat-hc-designates-nine-judges-for-trial-in-2002-gujarat-riot-cases-46884-2009-05-07%5C%22%3Erecommended%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20SIT%20must%20form%20a%20special%20witness%20protection%20cell%20considering%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20the%20nine%20cases%20that%20it%20was%20dealing%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnprotected%2C%20uncertain%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammed%20Abdul%20Hameed%20Sheikh%20lives%20in%20Ahmedabad%E2%80%99s%20Citizen%20Nagar%2C%20an%20area%20which%20is%20particularly%20distinguishable%20because%20of%20its%20rugged%20roads%2C%20worn%20out%20signboards%2C%20overwhelming%20stench%20of%20chemicals%20and%20heaps%20of%20garbage%20which%20cast%20a%20shadow%20on%20the%20life%20of%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20area.%20Citizen%20Nagar%20houses%20more%20than%2050%20Muslim%20families%20who%20were%20displaced%20in%20the%202002%20riots%20and%20have%20been%20living%20here%20for%20the%20past%2022%20years%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22114403%2FIMG_3394.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22114403%2FIMG_3394.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22114403%2FIMG_3394-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22114403%2FIMG_3394-1024x576.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693949%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EWitnesses%20of%20the%20Gujarat%20Riots%20have%20been%20living%20under%20police%20protection%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20now.%20Photo%3A%20Tarushi%20Aswani%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%2C%20also%20a%20witness%2C%20feels%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20withdraw%20security%20of%20the%20witnesses%20was%20%E2%80%98planned%E2%80%99%20to%20expose%20them%20to%20vulnerabilities%20that%20are%20associated%20with%20their%20lives%20as%20being%20witnesses%20to%20crimes%20committed%20against%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWho%20will%20listen%20to%20us%3F%20If%20we%20urge%20them%20to%20restore%20our%20security%20cover%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20it%20will%20make%20a%20difference%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sheikh%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%E2%80%99s%20house%20in%20Citizen%20Nagar%20has%20two%20identities%2C%20one%20is%20his%20address%20and%20the%20other%20is%20termed%20%E2%80%9CCISF%2022%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20label%20his%20house%20wears%20for%20belonging%20to%20a%20protected%20witness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20principal%20city%20sessions%20judge%20Jyotsna%20Yagnik%2C%20who%20had%20convicted%2032%20of%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20Naroda%20Patiya%20case%20involving%20the%20massacre%20of%2097%20people%2C%20is%20also%20among%20those%20who%20have%20lost%20police%20protection.%20She%20had%20two%20layers%20of%20security%20assigned%20to%20her%20after%20she%20received%20threats.%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20Yagnik%2C%20who%20refrained%20from%20commenting%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Twenty-Five%20Years%20Ago%2C%20a%20Murder%20Most%20Foul%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fgraham-staines-murder-25-years%5C%22%3ETwenty-Five%20Years%20Ago%2C%20a%20Murder%20Most%20Foul%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Ram%20Mandir%20is%20a%20reminder%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2027%2C%202002%2C%20a%20train%20carrying%20Hindu%20pilgrims%20returning%20from%20Ayodhya%20stopped%20at%20Godhra%2C%20a%20small%20town%20in%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20Panchmahal%20district%2C%20about%20150%20km%20from%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20capital%2C%20Gandhinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20an%20alleged%20scuffle%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%2C%20details%20of%20which%20remain%20unclear%20to%20this%20day%2C%20it%20is%20said%20that%20the%20train%20was%20set%20ablaze%2C%20reportedly%20killing%2059%20Hindu%20pilgrims.%20The%20Gujarat%20state%20government%2C%20then%20headed%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20said%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20dead%20were%20%3Cem%3Ekarsevaks%3C%2Fem%3E%20(volunteers)%20who%20had%20gone%20to%20Ayodhya%20to%20campaign%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20temple%20dedicated%20to%20Hindu%20God%20Ram%20at%20the%20exact%20site%20where%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20was%20demolished%20by%20a%20Hindu%20mob%20in%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20news%20of%20the%20burning%20of%20the%20train%20at%20Godhra%20spread%2C%20it%20was%20followed%20by%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2016%2F6%2F17%2Findia-court-jails-11-for-life-over-massacre-of-muslims%5C%22%3Eworst%20religious%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20independent%20India%E2%80%99s%20history%2C%20in%20which%20nearly%202%2C000%20people%20were%20killed%2C%20hundreds%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Ffeatures%2F2019%2F5%2F21%2Fgujarat-riots-gang-rape-survivor-receives-justice-after-17-years%5C%22%3Ewomen%20raped%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20thousands%20of%20homes%20and%20mosques%20destroyed%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20her%20own%20experience%20%2CBano%20said%3Cem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CMaahol%20waisa%20hi%20bann%20raha%20hai%2C%20wahi%20jaloos%2C%20wahi%20bhagwa%20jhande%2C%20humein%20ander%20se%20darr%20lagta%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(The%20same%20atmosphere%20is%20being%20built%20up%20today%2C%20the%20same%20saffron%20flags%2C%20we%20are%20scared).%E2%80%9D%C2%A0She%20identified%20right-wing%20extremists%20in%20the%20Naroda%20Patiya%20case%20(FIR%20100%2F02)%20which%20is%20currently%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22114418%2FIMG_3391.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22114418%2FIMG_3391.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.th