%20Dhoni%2C%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20Mithali%20Raj%2C%20Harmanpreet%20Kaur%2C%20and%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20have%20also%20been%20invited%20to%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Pran%20Pratishtha'%20ceremony%20will%20begin%20at%2012%3A30%20p.m.%20amid%20tight%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20Trust%20announced%20on%20Sunday%20that%20the%20'Pran%20Pratishtha'%20ceremony%20will%20be%20marked%20by%20a%20dazzling%20musical%20event%20titled%20'Mangal%20Dhwani'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20temple%20is%20constructed%20in%20the%20traditional%20Nagara%20style.%20Its%20length%20(east-west)%20is%20380%20feet%2C%20its%20width%20is%20250%20feet%20and%20its%20height%20is%20161%20feet.%20It%20is%20supported%20by%20a%20total%20of%20392%20pillars%20and%2044%20doors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pillars%20and%20walls%20of%20the%20temple%20showcase%20intricately%20sculpted%20depictions%20of%20Hindu%20deities%2C%20gods%2C%20and%20goddesses.%20In%20the%20main%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%2C%20the%20childhood%20form%20of%20Bhagwan%20Shri%20Ram%20(the%20idol%20of%20Shri%20Ramlalla)%20has%20been%20placed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20entrance%20to%20the%20temple%20is%20situated%20on%20the%20eastern%20side%2C%20which%20can%20be%20approached%20by%20ascending%2032%20stairs%20through%20the%20Singh%20Dwar.%20There%20are%20a%20total%20of%20five%20Mandaps%20(halls)%20in%20the%20mandir%3A%20Nritya%20Mandap%2C%20Rang%20Mandap%2C%20Sabha%20Mandap%2C%20Prathana%20Mandap%20and%20Kirtan%20Mandap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENear%20the%20temple%20is%20a%20historic%20well%20(Sita%20koop)%2C%20dating%20back%20to%20the%20ancient%20era.%20In%20the%20southwestern%20part%20of%20the%20temple's%20complex%2C%20at%20Kuber%20Tila%2C%20the%20ancient%20temple%20of%20Bhagwan%20Shiv%20has%20been%20restored%2C%20along%20with%20the%20installation%20of%20a%20statue%20of%20Jatayu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20of%20the%20temple%20has%20been%20constructed%20with%20a%2014-meter-thick%20layer%20of%20roller-compacted%20concrete%20(RCC)%2C%20giving%20it%20the%20appearance%20of%20artificial%20rock.%20No%20iron%20is%20used%20anywhere%20in%20the%20temple.%20For%20protection%20against%20ground%20moisture%2C%20a%2021-foot-high%20plinth%20has%20been%20constructed%20using%20granite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20ANI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705903860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F0pmunk1o_tendulkar_625x300_22_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwatch-sachin-tendulkar-saina-nehwal-anil-kumble-other-sports-stars-reach-ayodhy-4908831%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20cricket%20legend%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20reached%20the%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20to%20attend%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20ceremony.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A78%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Duchess%20of%20York%2C%20Sarah%20Ferguson%20diagnosed%20with%20skin%20cancer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705903818000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107044928%2Cimgsize-793780.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Flife-style%2Fhealth-fitness%2Fhealth-news%2Fduchess-of-york-sarah-ferguson-diagnosed-with-skin-cancer%2Farticleshow%2F107044950.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sarah%20Ferguson%2C%20former%20wife%20of%20Prince%20Andrew%2C%20diagnosed%20with%20skin%20cancer.%20She%20had%20surgery%20for%20breast%20tumor%20and%20was%20later%20diagnosed%20with%20malignant%20melanoma.%20Several%20moles%20were%20removed%20and%20analyzed%2C%20one%20of%20which%20was%20cancerous.%20Ferguson%20remains%20in%20good%20spirits%20and%20emphasizes%20the%20importance%20of%20regular%20skin%20checks.%20Early%20signs%20inclu