ce%20for%20president%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side-by-side%20image%20of%20ChatGPT's%20logo%20next%20to%202024%20presidential%20hopeful%20Dean%20Phillips%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ada1ac617029e90a5edd5e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOpenAI%20on%20Friday%20suspended%20a%20developer%20who%20had%20created%20Dean.Bot%2C%20a%20ChatGPT-powered%20AI%20bot%20intended%20to%20support%20Dean%20Phillips'%202024%20presidential%20campaign.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20super%20PAC%20for%20presidential%20hopeful%20Dean%20Phillips%20created%20a%20ChatGPT-powered%20bot%20to%20mimic%20him.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20banned%20the%20developer's%20account%2C%20per%20WaPo%2C%20for%20violating%20rules%20about%20using%20ChatGPT%20for%20politics.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDespite%20OpenAI's%20rules%2C%20Dean.Bot%20won't%20be%20the%20last%20AI%20creation%20we%20see%20this%20election%20season.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELate%20Friday%20night%2C%20OpenAI%20suspended%20a%20developer%20who%20had%20created%20Dean.Bot%20%E2%80%94%20a%20ChatGPT-powered%20chatbot%20intended%20to%20support%20Minnesota%20Rep.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdean-phillips-democratic-presidential-nomination-joe-biden-congress-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDean%20Phillips%3C%2Fa%3E'%202024%20presidential%20campaign%20%E2%80%94%20for%20violating%20new%20rules%20preventing%20lobbyists%20and%20candidates%20from%20using%20ChatGPT%20for%20politics%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Ftechnology%2F2024%2F01%2F20%2Fopenai-dean-phillips-ban-chatgpt%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDean.Bot%20conversed%20with%20constituents%20in%20real%20time%20while%20mimicking%20the%20long%20shot%20Democratic%20challenger%20for%20president%2C%20using%20an%20AI-generated%20version%20of%20Phillips'%20voice%20to%20respond%20to%20user%20questions%2C%20like%20why%20Democrats%20shouldn't%20be%20throwing%20their%20weight%20behind%20incumbent%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20in%20the%202024%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20I%20respect%20President%20Biden%2C%20the%20data%20and%20conversations%20with%20Americans%20across%20the%20country%20indicates%20a%20strong%20desire%20for%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20WaPo%20reported%20Dean.Bot%20responded%20in%20an%20AI-generated%20voice%20that%20sounded%20like%20Phillips'%20but%20had%20an%20unusual%20cadence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhillips'%20background%20is%20in%20business.%20He%20ran%20his%20family's%20distilling%20company%20between%202000%20and%202012%20before%20pivoting%20to%20run%20Talenti%2C%20the%20popular%20gelato%20company%20he'd%20invested%20in%20until%20it%20was%20sold%20in%202014.%20He%20has%20represented%20Minnesota%20since%202019%20and%20launched%20his%20campaign%20to%20challenge%20Biden%20in%20October%20last%20year.%20However%2C%20his%20polling%20numbers%20haven't%20indicated%20he'd%20be%20a%20significant%20threat%20to%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20creation%20of%20Dean.Bot%20was%20funded%20by%20the%20Super%20PAC%20We%20Deserve%20Better%2C%20WaPo%20reported.%20The%20PAC%20then%20partnered%20with%20AI%20developer%20Delphi%20to%20build%20the%20bot.%20Delphi's%20account%20was%20suspended%20for%20violating%20the%20political%20rules%20late%20Friday%2C%20just%20a%20day%20after%20WaPo%20wrote%20about%20the%20creation%20of%20Dean.Bot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20earlier%20this%20month%20announced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopenai.com%2Fblog%2Fhow-openai-is-approaching-2024-worldwide-elections%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E%20preventing%20developers%20from%20building%20applications%20using%20its%20ChatGPT%20software%20intended%20for%20political%20campaigning%20or%20lobbying%2C%20saying%20the%20platform%20is%20%26quot%3Bstill%20working%20to%20understand%20how%20effective%20our%20tools%20might%20be%20for%20personalized%20persuasion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-usage-policy-chatgpt-military-purposes-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Phillips'%202024%20presidential%20campaign%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20OpenAI's%20new%20rules%2C%20Dean.Bot%20won't%20be%20the%20last%20AI%20creation%20we%20see%20this%20election%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fpolicy%2Ftechnology%2F4309795-tech-companies-craft-ai-election-rules-government-regulation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Hill%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20Google%20and%20Meta%20have%20crafted%20policies%20requiring%20politicians%20and%20lobbyists%20to%20label%20content%20created%20by%20generative%20AI%20in%20campaign-related%20materials%20in%20response%20to%20a%20surge%20of%20AI-created%20content%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-deepfake%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeepfakes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20misleading%20audio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outlet%20reported%20that%20several%20lawmakers%2C%20including%20Sen.%20Amy%20Klobuchar%20and%20Sen.%20Susan%20Collins%2C%20have%20also%20introduced%20congressional%20proposals%20to%20address%20AI%20use%20in%20advertisements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20viewers%20will%20need%20to%20keep%20their%20eyes%20peeled%20for%20AI-generated%20content%20this%20election%20season%20until%20those%20measures%20pass%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0if%20they%20pass%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-openai-dean-phillips-campaign-chatbot-deanbot-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3