igcaption%3EThe%20sitting%20room.%3Cp%3EMcKinley%20Manor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20tedious%20part%20of%20the%20restoration%20process%20was%20working%20on%20the%20exterior%2C%20which%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20decorative%20detail.%20Sometimes%20Heemstra%20even%20had%20to%20resort%20to%20using%20dental%20tools%20to%20scrape%20the%20old%20paint%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20hardest%20part%20is%20getting%20into%20the%20groove%20of%20learning%20a%20new%20skill%2C%20she%20added.%20That%20said%2C%20she%20enjoys%20the%20challenge%20of%20trying%20new%20things%2C%20such%20as%20glazing%20windows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20tell%20me%20I%20can't%20learn%20something%20new.%20I'm%20going%20to%20figure%20it%20out.%20It%20may%20not%20be%20perfect%20but%20I'll%20learn%20as%20I%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20Heemstra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20of%20the%20bedrooms%20in%20the%20house.%20The%20room%20has%20a%20light%20blue%20color%20theme%20and%20features%20a%20bee%20wallpaper.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659cf9196979d7371821857e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20bedrooms%20in%20the%20house.%3Cp%3EMcKinley%20Manor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlready%20rented%20it%20once%20out%20before%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20the%20house%20isn't%20ready%20on%20the%20outside%2C%20Heemstra%20says%20that%20she's%20already%20rented%20the%20place%20out%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20for%20the%20fianc%C3%A9e%20of%20my%20friend's%20son%20to%20use%20while%20her%20bridal%20party%20got%20ready%20for%20their%20wedding%20in%20September%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20nice%20to%20be%20able%20to%20provide%20a%20beautiful%20spot%20for%20friends%20and%20a%20nice%20dry%20run%20to%20see%20how%20the%20space%20would%20work%20out%20for%20them.%20%26qu