0will%20be%20thrown%20open%20to%20people%20after%20the%20long%20high-profile%20consecration%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20slated%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20entire%20ritual%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ejajman%3C%2Fem%3E%20(master%20of%20ceremonies)%E2%80%99%20himself%2C%20the%20controversies%20that%20followed%20apparently%20led%20him%20to%20make%20room%20for%20a%20new%20jajman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20questions%20raised%20by%20top%20religious%20functionaries%20including%20the%20Shankaracharyas%20(the%20tallest%20priests%20under%20the%20Hindu%20order)%20were%20that%20the%20jajman%20had%20to%20necessarily%20be%20a%20Hindu%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20who%20were%20required%20to%20live%20the%20life%20of%20a%20saint%20for%2011%20days%20before%20performing%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Epran%20pratishtha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(consecration)%E2%80%99%20ceremony.%20Evidently%2C%20this%20criticism%20left%C2%A0%20Modi%20with%20no%20option%20but%20to%20opt%20out.%20His%20officials%20declared%20that%20since%20it%20would%20not%20be%20possible%20for%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20set%20aside%20all%20his%20official%20obligations%20for%2011%20days%2C%20hence%20a%20a%20local%20person%2C%20Anil%20Misra%2C%20and%20his%20wife%20Usha%20were%20nominated%20as%20the%20new%20jajman%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20practicing%20homeopathic%20doctor%2C%20Misra%20was%20handpicked%20by%20Ram%20Janmbhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20Trust%20secretary%20Champat%20Rai%2C%20who%20has%20been%20handling%20the%20temple%20construction%20work%20ever%20since%20the%20trust%20was%20formed%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20following%20orders%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20November%202019.%20Rai%E2%80%99s%20criticism%20on%20the%20issue%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20once%20again%20led%20the%20Trust%20top%20brass%20to%20get%2014%20more%20jajmans%20to%20jointly%20perform%20the%20pran%20pratishtha%2C%20where%20Modi%20will%20remain%20the%20%E2%80%9Csymbolic%20jajman%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%20Significantly%2C%20the%20Trust%20is%20headed%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20former%20principal%20secretary%20Nripendra%20Misra%2C%20a%201966-batch%20UP%20cadre%20IAS%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20such%2C%20the%20ceremony%20will%20eventually%20be%20carried%20out%20by%20a%20total%20of%2016%20jajmans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21192102%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-1.25.08-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21192102%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-1.25.08-PM.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21192102%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-1.25.08-PM-300x226.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F21192102%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-1.25.08-PM-1024x771.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-693913%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22904%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Ram%20mandir%20on%20Sunday.%20Photo%3A%20Shruti%20Sonkar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Trust%20sources%2C%20the%2014%20jajmans%20finally%20added%20represent%20different%20states%20including%20Rajasthan%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Assam%20and%20Haryana%20besides%20UP%2C%20and%20each%20one%20of%20them%20belongs%20to%20a%20different%20caste%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Egarbh%20grah%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20temple%20was%20washed%20with%20water%20kept%20in%2081%20%3Cem%3Ekalsas%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(metal%20containers).%20This%20water%20is%20stated%20to%20have%20been%20drawn%20from%20different%20rivers%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%