gh-bollywood-dialogues%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMumbai%3C%2Fa%3E%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20knocking%20on%20his%20door%20many%20times%2C%20there%20was%20no%20response.%20Busy%20with%20his%20rounds%2C%20the%20milkman%20left%20the%20milk%20to%20a%20neighbour.%20After%20some%20time%2C%20Usman%2C%20the%20watchman%20of%20Choonawala%E2%80%99s%20M%2FS%20Car%20Mart%2C%20came%20to%20deliver%20milk%20bottles%20at%20his%20residence.%20Once%20again%2C%20he%20rang%20the%20bell%20but%20no%20response%20was%20forthcoming.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20cook%20Sayed%20Ahmed%2C%20who%20was%20sleeping%20in%20the%20common%20passage%2C%20woke%20up%20and%20saw%20smoke%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20windows%20of%20the%20flat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Mumbai-based%20journalist%2C%20author%20and%20local%20historian%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdhavalkulkarni%2Fstatus%2F1745164531842888077%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDhaval%20Kulkarni%3C%2Fa%3E%20notes%20in%20his%20recent%20thread%20on%20X%20(Twitter)%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20main%20door%20of%20the%20flat%20was%20slightly%20ajar%20and%20he%20went%20in%20with%20Usman.%20They%20saw%20fire%20in%20the%20passage%20leading%20to%20the%20kitchen.%20This%20fire%20in%20newspapers%20and%20clothes%20was%20doused%20using%20buckets%20of%20water.%20Once%20the%20fire%20subsided%2C%20they%20were%20terrified%20to%20see%20human%20legs%20under%20the%20newspapers%20in%20a%20scorched%20condition.%20The%20watchman%20ran%20to%20the%20nearby%20Gamdevi%20police%20station%20and%20informed%20PSI%20(Police%20Sub-Inspector)%20Shivaji%20Deshmukh%2C%20who%20was%20on%20duty.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FMumbai-Murder-Choonawala-Collage-1705586378.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%