%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20few%20months%2C%20I%20observed%20that%20Rajasthan%20did%20not%20have%20a%20single%20unit%20that%20manufactured%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329202%2Fgwalior-professor-nidhi-katare-becomes-successful-mushroom-farmer-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emushroom%20spawns%3C%2Fa%3E.%20People%20were%20dependent%20on%20states%20like%20Himachal%2C%20Haryana%2C%20and%20Delhi%20to%20source%20the%20seeds.%20I%20saw%20this%20as%20a%20perfect%20opportunity%20that%20would%20help%20me%20stand%20out%20in%20the%20crowd%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%2C%20Shanker%20sourced%20the%20mother%20culture%20from%20ICAR%2C%20Solan%20and%20set%20up%20a%20temporary%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98jugaad%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(make-do%20lab)%20in%20the%20garage%20of%20his%20house%20to%20cultivate%20spawns%20on%20a%20trial%20basis.%20Meanwhile%2C%20he%20also%20managed%20to%20get%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%209%20lakhs%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20MUDRA%20Yojana.%20With%20the%20loan%20amount%20and%20financial%20support%20from%20family%20and%20friends%2C%20he%20worked%20on%20establishing%20a%20dedicated%20lab%20spread%20across%20an%20area%20of%209%2C000%20sq-ft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20lab%2C%20he%20introduced%20advanced%20pieces%20of%20machinery%20like%20seed%20germination%20chambers%2C%20vertical%20autoclaves%2C%20and%20a%20laminar%20airflow%20cabinet%20to%20provide%20a%20sterile%20working%20environment%20for%20better%20productivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20after%20five%20years%20of%20research%20and%20development%2C%20Shanker%20officially%20launched%20his%20company%20which%20he%20runs%20along%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20Kanchan%20Meena.%20With%20the%20help%20of%20social%20media%2C%20he%20started%20getting%20orders%20for%20mushroom%20spawns%20in%20bulk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Shanker%20produces%20up%20to%2080%20tonnes%20of%20mushr